public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        Map<Integer, Integer> teamScores = new HashMap<>();
        Set<Integer> scoreSet = new HashSet<>();

        while (true) {
            String line = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.equals("")) continue;
            String[] parts = line.split(",");
            int p = Integer.parseInt(parts[0]);
            int s = Integer.parseInt(parts[1]);
            if (p == 0 && s == 0) break;
            teamScores.put(p, s);
            scoreSet.add(s);
        }

        List<Integer> sortedScores = new ArrayList<>(scoreSet);
        sortedScores.sort(Collections.reverseOrder());
        Map<Integer, Integer> scoreToRank = new HashMap<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < sortedScores.size(); i++) {
            scoreToRank.put(sortedScores.get(i), i + 1);
        }

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String qLine = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (qLine.equals("")) continue;
            int q = Integer.parseInt(qLine);
            int score = teamScores.get(q);
            System.out.println(scoreToRank.get(score));

train/1/chatgpt_p00063_1P.java: 1-26 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int count = 0;
        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String s = sc.nextLine();
            if (isPalindrome(s)) {
                count++;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(count);
    }

    private static boolean isPalindrome(String s) {
        int n = s.length();
        for (int i = 0; i < n / 2; i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) != s.charAt(n - 1 - i)) {
                return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p00063_3P.java: 1-26 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int palindromeCount = 0;
        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine();
            if (isPalindrome(line)) {
                palindromeCount++;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(palindromeCount);
    }

    private static boolean isPalindrome(String s) {
        int n = s.length();
        for (int i = 0; i < n / 2; i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) != s.charAt(n - 1 - i)) {
                return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int winnerNum = 0;
        int winnerFish = -1;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int num = sc.nextInt();
            int fish = sc.nextInt();

                winnerFish = fish;
                winnerNum = num;

        }

    }

            int count = 0;

                for (int b = 0; b <= 1000; b++) {

train/1/chatgpt_p00100_3P.java: 1-35 
import java.util.*;

public class SaleResult {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            LinkedHashMap<Integer, Long> sales = new LinkedHashMap<>();

            for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                int id = sc.nextInt();
                int p = sc.nextInt();
                int q = sc.nextInt();
                long amount = (long) p * q;
                sales.put(id, sales.getOrDefault(id, 0L) + amount);
            }

            boolean found = false;
            for (Map.Entry<Integer, Long> entry : sales.entrySet()) {
                if (entry.getValue() >= 1_000_000L) {
                    System.out.println(entry.getKey());
                    found = true;
                }
            }
            if (!found) {
                System.out.println("NA");
            }
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p00102_2P.java: 1-39 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int[][] table = new int[n][n];
            int[] rowSum = new int[n];
            int[] colSum = new int[n];
            int totalSum = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                    table[i][j] = sc.nextInt();
                    rowSum[i] += table[i][j];
                    colSum[j] += table[i][j];
                    totalSum += table[i][j];
                }
            }

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                    System.out.printf("%5d", table[i][j]);
                }
                System.out.printf("%5d\n", rowSum[i]);
            }

            for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                System.out.printf("%5d", colSum[j]);
            }
            System.out.printf("%5d\n", totalSum);
        }
    }
}

Class 145:   3 fragments, nominal size 22 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p00105_0P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.*;

public class BookIndex {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        TreeMap<String, TreeSet<Integer>> index = new TreeMap<>();
        while (sc.hasNext()) {
            String word = sc.next();
            if (!sc.hasNextInt()) break;
            int page = sc.nextInt();
            index.computeIfAbsent(word, k -> new TreeSet<>()).add(page);
        }
        for (String word : index.keySet()) {
            System.out.println(word);
            TreeSet<Integer> pages = index.get(word);
            StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
            for (int p : pages) {
                sb.append(p).append(" ");
            }
            System.out.println(sb.toString().trim());
        }
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p00105_3P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.*;

public class BookIndex {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        TreeMap<String, TreeSet<Integer>> index = new TreeMap<>();
        while (sc.hasNext()) {
            String word = sc.next();
            if (!sc.hasNextInt()) break;
            int page = sc.nextInt();
            index.computeIfAbsent(word, k -> new TreeSet<>()).add(page);
        }
        for (String word : index.keySet()) {
            System.out.println(word);
            TreeSet<Integer> pages = index.get(word);
            StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
            for (int p : pages) {
                sb.append(p).append(" ");
            }
            System.out.println(sb.toString().trim());
        }
    }
}

public class BookIndex {

Class 147:   3 fragments, nominal size 25 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p00159_0P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int minP = 0;
            double minDiff = Double.MAX_VALUE;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int p = sc.nextInt();
                int h = sc.nextInt();
                int w = sc.nextInt();
                double hm = h / 100.0;
                double bmi = w / (hm * hm);
                double diff = Math.abs(bmi - 22);

                if (diff < minDiff || (Math.abs(diff - minDiff) < 1e-8 && p < minP)) {
                    minDiff = diff;
                    minP = p;
                }
            }
            System.out.println(minP);
        }
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p00159_4P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int bestP = 0;
            double minDiff = Double.MAX_VALUE;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int p = sc.nextInt();
                int h = sc.nextInt();
                int w = sc.nextInt();
                double heightM = h / 100.0;
                double bmi = w / (heightM * heightM);
                double diff = Math.abs(bmi - 22.0);

                if (diff < minDiff || (Math.abs(diff - minDiff) < 1e-9 && p < bestP)) {
                    minDiff = diff;
                    bestP = p;
                }
            }
            System.out.println(bestP);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int ansP = 0;
            double minDiff = Double.MAX_VALUE;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int p = sc.nextInt();
                int h = sc.nextInt();
                int w = sc.nextInt();

                double h_m = h / 100.0;
                double bmi = w / (h_m * h_m);

                double diff = Math.abs(bmi - 22);

                if (diff < minDiff || (Math.abs(diff - minDiff) < 1e-8 && p < ansP)) {
                    minDiff = diff;
                    ansP = p;
                }
            }
            System.out.println(ansP);
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p00217_3P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int maxPatient = -1;
            int maxDist = -1;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int p = sc.nextInt();
                int d1 = sc.nextInt();
                int d2 = sc.nextInt();
                int sum = d1 + d2;
                if (sum > maxDist) {
                    maxDist = sum;
                    maxPatient = p;
                }
            }
            System.out.println(maxPatient + " " + maxDist);
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p00219_3P.java: 1-29 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            if (!sc.hasNext()) break;
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;
            int[] count = new int[10];
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int t = sc.nextInt();
                count[t]++;
            }
            for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
                if (count[i] == 0) {
                    System.out.println("-");
                } else {
                    for (int j = 0; j < count[i]; j++) {
                        System.out.print("*");
                    }
                    System.out.println();
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int x1 = sc.nextInt();
                int y1 = sc.nextInt();
                int z1 = sc.nextInt();
                int w1 = sc.nextInt();
                int x2 = sc.nextInt();
                int y2 = sc.nextInt();
                int z2 = sc.nextInt();
                int w2 = sc.nextInt();

                int z3 = x1 * z2 - y1 * w2 + z1 * x2 + w1 * y2;
                int w3 = x1 * w2 + y1 * z2 - z1 * y2 + w1 * x2;

                System.out.println(x3 + " " + y3 + " " + z3 + " " + w3);
            }
        }

                int y1 = sc.nextInt();
                int z1 = sc.nextInt();
                int w1 = sc.nextInt();
                int x2 = sc.nextInt();
                int y2 = sc.nextInt();
                int z2 = sc.nextInt();
                int w2 = sc.nextInt();

                int x3 = x1 * x2 - y1 * y2 - z1 * z2 - w1 * w2;
                int y3 = x1 * y2 + y1 * x2 + z1 * w2 - w1 * z2;
                int z3 = x1 * z2 - y1 * w2 + z1 * x2 + w1 * y2;
                int w3 = x1 * w2 + y1 * z2 - z1 * y2 + w1 * x2;

                System.out.println(x3 + " " + y3 + " " + z3 + " " + w3);
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p00423_3P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int scoreA = 0, scoreB = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int a = sc.nextInt();
                int b = sc.nextInt();

                if (a > b) {
                    scoreA += a + b;
                } else if (a < b) {
                    scoreB += a + b;
                } else {
                    scoreA += a;
                    scoreB += b;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(scoreA + " " + scoreB);
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p00439_2P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0 && k == 0) break;
            int[] a = new int[n];
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) a[i] = sc.nextInt();

            int sum = 0;
            for (int i = 0; i < k; i++) sum += a[i];
            int max = sum;

            for (int i = k; i < n; i++) {
                sum += a[i] - a[i - k];
                if (sum > max) max = sum;
            }
            System.out.println(max);
        }
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p00439_3P.java: 1-27 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0 && k == 0) break;

            int[] a = new int[n];
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) a[i] = sc.nextInt();

            int sum = 0;
            for (int i = 0; i < k; i++) sum += a[i];

            int maxSum = sum;
            for (int i = k; i < n; i++) {
                sum += a[i] - a[i - k];
                if (sum > maxSum) maxSum = sum;
            }
            System.out.println(maxSum);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        for(int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            int sh = sc.nextInt();
            int sm = sc.nextInt();
            int ss = sc.nextInt();
            int eh = sc.nextInt();
            int em = sc.nextInt();
            int es = sc.nextInt();

            int startSec = sh * 3600 + sm * 60 + ss;
            int endSec = eh * 3600 + em * 60 + es;
            int diff = endSec - startSec;

            int h = diff / 3600;
            diff %= 3600;
            int m = diff / 60;
            int s = diff % 60;

            System.out.println(h + " " + m + " " + s);
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p00593_4P.java: 1-42 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int caseNum = 1;
        while (true) {
            int N = sc.nextInt();
            if (N == 0) break;
            int[][] mat = new int[N][N];
            int cnt = 1;
            for (int s = 0; s <= 2 * (N - 1); s++) {
                if (s % 2 == 0) {
                    for (int i = 0; i <= s; i++) {
                        int x = i;
                        int y = s - i;
                        if (x < N && y < N) {
                            mat[x][y] = cnt++;
                        }
                    }
                } else {
                    for (int i = 0; i <= s; i++) {
                        int x = s - i;
                        int y = i;
                        if (x < N && y < N) {
                            mat[x][y] = cnt++;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            System.out.println("Case " + caseNum + ":");
            for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
                for (int j = 0; j < N; j++) {
                    System.out.printf("%3d", mat[i][j]);
                }
                System.out.println();
            }
            caseNum++;
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static int gcd(int a, int b) {
        while(b != 0) {
            int temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        while(sc.hasNextInt()) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            System.out.println(gcd(a, b));
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p00705_0P.java: 1-38 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        while (true) {
            int N = sc.nextInt();
            int Q = sc.nextInt();
            if (N == 0 && Q == 0) break;

            int[] dateCount = new int[100];

            for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
                int M = sc.nextInt();
                for (int j = 0; j < M; j++) {
                    int date = sc.nextInt();
                    dateCount[date]++;
                }
            }

            int maxCount = 0;
            int bestDate = 0;
            for (int date = 1; date < 100; date++) {
                if (dateCount[date] > maxCount) {
                    maxCount = dateCount[date];
                    bestDate = date;
                }
            }

            if (maxCount >= Q) {
                System.out.println(bestDate);
            } else {
                System.out.println(0);
            }
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static int fib(int n) {
        if (n == 0 || n == 1) return 1;
        int a = 1, b = 1;
        for (int i = 2; i <= n; i++) {
            int c = a + b;
            a = b;
            b = c;
        }
        return b;
    }
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        System.out.println(fib(n));
    }
}

Class 171:   2 fragments, nominal size 53 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p02243_1P.java: 1-60 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static class Edge {
        int to, cost;
        Edge(int to, int cost) {
            this.to = to;
            this.cost = cost;
        }
    }

    static class Node implements Comparable<Node> {
        int v, dist;
        Node(int v, int dist) {
            this.v = v;
            this.dist = dist;
        }
        public int compareTo(Node o) {
            return Integer.compare(this.dist, o.dist);
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        List<Edge>[] graph = new ArrayList[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) graph[i] = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int u = sc.nextInt();
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                int v = sc.nextInt();
                int c = sc.nextInt();
                graph[u].add(new Edge(v, c));
            }
        }

        int[] dist = new int[n];
        Arrays.fill(dist, Integer.MAX_VALUE);
        dist[0] = 0;
        PriorityQueue<Node> pq = new PriorityQueue<>();
        pq.offer(new Node(0, 0));

        while (!pq.isEmpty()) {
            Node cur = pq.poll();
            if (cur.dist > dist[cur.v]) continue;
            for (Edge e : graph[cur.v]) {
                if (dist[e.to] > dist[cur.v] + e.cost) {
                    dist[e.to] = dist[cur.v] + e.cost;
                    pq.offer(new Node(e.to, dist[e.to]));
                }
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            System.out.println(i + " " + dist[i]);
        }
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p02243_4P.java: 1-61 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static class Edge {
        int to, cost;
        Edge(int to, int cost) {
            this.to = to;
            this.cost = cost;
        }
    }

    static class Node implements Comparable<Node> {
        int id, dist;
        Node(int id, int dist) {
            this.id = id;
            this.dist = dist;
        }
        public int compareTo(Node o) {
            return Integer.compare(this.dist, o.dist);
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        List<Edge>[] adj = new ArrayList[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) adj[i] = new ArrayList<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int u = sc.nextInt();
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                int v = sc.nextInt();
                int c = sc.nextInt();
                adj[u].add(new Edge(v, c));
            }
        }

        int[] dist = new int[n];
        Arrays.fill(dist, Integer.MAX_VALUE);
        dist[0] = 0;
        PriorityQueue<Node> pq = new PriorityQueue<>();
        pq.offer(new Node(0, 0));

        while (!pq.isEmpty()) {
            Node curr = pq.poll();
            if (curr.dist > dist[curr.id]) continue;
            for (Edge e : adj[curr.id]) {
                if (dist[e.to] > dist[curr.id] + e.cost) {
                    dist[e.to] = dist[curr.id] + e.cost;
                    pq.offer(new Node(e.to, dist[e.to]));
                }
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            System.out.println(i + " " + dist[i]);
        }
    }
}

Class 172:   2 fragments, nominal size 48 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p02262_1P.java: 1-54 
import java.io.*;
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static int cnt = 0;
    static ArrayList<Integer> G = new ArrayList<>();

    static void insertionSort(int[] A, int n, int g) {
        for (int i = g; i < n; i++) {
            int v = A[i];
            int j = i - g;
            while (j >= 0 && A[j] > v) {
                A[j + g] = A[j];
                j = j - g;
                cnt++;
            }
            A[j + g] = v;
        }
    }

    static void shellSort(int[] A, int n) {
        G.clear();
        for (int h = 1; h <= n; ) {
            G.add(h);
            h = 3 * h + 1;
        }
        Collections.reverse(G);
        for (int i = 0; i < G.size(); i++) {
            insertionSort(A, n, G.get(i));
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        BufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(System.in));
        int n = Integer.parseInt(br.readLine());
        int[] A = new int[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            A[i] = Integer.parseInt(br.readLine());
        }
        shellSort(A, n);

        System.out.println(G.size());
        for (int i = 0; i < G.size(); i++) {
            System.out.print(G.get(i));
            if (i != G.size() - 1) System.out.print(" ");
        }
        System.out.println();
        System.out.println(cnt);
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            System.out.println(A[i]);
        }
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p02262_3P.java: 1-53 
import java.io.*;
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static int cnt = 0;
    static ArrayList<Integer> G = new ArrayList<>();

    static void insertionSort(int[] A, int n, int g) {
        for (int i = g; i < n; i++) {
            int v = A[i];
            int j = i - g;
            while (j >= 0 && A[j] > v) {
                A[j + g] = A[j];
                j = j - g;
                cnt++;
            }
            A[j + g] = v;
        }
    }

    static void shellSort(int[] A, int n) {
        G.clear();
        for (int h = 1; h <= n; ) {
            G.add(h);
            h = 3 * h + 1;
        }
        Collections.reverse(G);
        for (int i = 0; i < G.size(); i++) {
            insertionSort(A, n, G.get(i));
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {
        BufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(System.in));
        int n = Integer.parseInt(br.readLine());
        int[] A = new int[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            A[i] = Integer.parseInt(br.readLine());
        }
        shellSort(A, n);
        System.out.println(G.size());
        for (int i = 0; i < G.size(); i++) {
            System.out.print(G.get(i));
            if (i != G.size() - 1) System.out.print(" ");
        }
        System.out.println();
        System.out.println(cnt);
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            System.out.println(A[i]);
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02288_3P.java: 1-47 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static int H;
    static int[] A;

    static void maxHeapify(int i) {
        int l = 2 * i;
        int r = 2 * i + 1;
        int largest;
        if (l <= H && A[l] > A[i]) {
            largest = l;
        } else {
            largest = i;
        }
        if (r <= H && A[r] > A[largest]) {
            largest = r;
        }
        if (largest != i) {
            int temp = A[i];
            A[i] = A[largest];
            A[largest] = temp;
            maxHeapify(largest);
        }
    }

    static void buildMaxHeap() {
        for (int i = H / 2; i >= 1; i--) {
            maxHeapify(i);
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        H = sc.nextInt();
        A = new int[H + 1];
        for (int i = 1; i <= H; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        buildMaxHeap();
        for (int i = 1; i <= H; i++) {
            System.out.print(" " + A[i]);
        }
        System.out.println();
    }
}

public class Main {
    static int H;
    static int[] A;

    static void maxHeapify(int i) {
        int l = 2 * i;
        int r = 2 * i + 1;
        int largest;
        if (l <= H && A[l] > A[i]) {
            largest = l;
        } else {
            largest = i;
        }
        if (r <= H && A[r] > A[largest]) {
            largest = r;
        }
        if (largest != i) {
            int temp = A[i];
            A[i] = A[largest];
            A[largest] = temp;
            maxHeapify(largest);
        }
    }

    static void buildMaxHeap() {
        for (int i = H / 2; i >= 1; i--) {
            maxHeapify(i);
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        H = sc.nextInt();
        A = new int[H + 1];
        for (int i = 1; i <= H; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        buildMaxHeap();
        for (int i = 1; i <= H; i++) {
            System.out.print(" " + A[i]);
        }

train/1/chatgpt_p02314_1P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int m = sc.nextInt();
        int[] coins = new int[m];
        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
            coins[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        int[] dp = new int[n + 1];
        Arrays.fill(dp, Integer.MAX_VALUE / 2);
        dp[0] = 0;
        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
            for (int coin : coins) {
                if (i - coin >= 0) {
                    dp[i] = Math.min(dp[i], dp[i - coin] + 1);
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(dp[n]);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02315_0P.java: 1-27 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int[] v = new int[N];
        int[] w = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            v[i] = sc.nextInt();
            w[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        int[] dp = new int[W + 1];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            for (int j = W; j >= w[i]; j--) {
                dp[j] = Math.max(dp[j], dp[j - w[i]] + v[i]);
            }
        }
        int max = 0;
        for (int x : dp) {
            if (x > max) max = x;
        }
        System.out.println(max);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02364_2P.java: 1-58 
import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    static class Edge implements Comparable<Edge> {
        int u, v, w;
        Edge(int u, int v, int w) {
            this.u = u;
            this.v = v;
            this.w = w;
        }
        public int compareTo(Edge o) {
            return Integer.compare(this.w, o.w);
        }
    }

    static class DSU {
        int[] parent, rank;
        DSU(int n) {
            parent = new int[n];
            rank = new int[n];
            for(int i=0;i<n;i++) parent[i]=i;
        }
        int find(int x) {
            if(parent[x]!=x) parent[x]=find(parent[x]);
            return parent[x];
        }
        boolean union(int x, int y) {
            int xr=find(x), yr=find(y);
            if(xr==yr) return false;
            if(rank[xr]<rank[yr]) parent[xr]=yr;
            else if(rank[xr]>rank[yr]) parent[yr]=xr;
            else {parent[yr]=xr; rank[xr]++;}
            return true;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int V = sc.nextInt(), E = sc.nextInt();
        Edge[] edges = new Edge[E];
        for(int i=0;i<E;i++) {
            int u = sc.nextInt(), v = sc.nextInt(), w = sc.nextInt();
            edges[i] = new Edge(u, v, w);
        }
        Arrays.sort(edges);
        DSU dsu = new DSU(V);
        long mst = 0;
        int cnt = 0;
        for(Edge e : edges) {
            if(dsu.union(e.u, e.v)) {
                mst += e.w;
                cnt++;
                if(cnt==V-1) break;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(mst);
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p02364_4P.java: 1-61 
import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    static class Edge implements Comparable<Edge> {
        int u, v, w;
        Edge(int u, int v, int w) {
            this.u = u;
            this.v = v;
            this.w = w;
        }
        public int compareTo(Edge other) {
            return Integer.compare(this.w, other.w);
        }
    }

    static class DSU {
        int[] parent, rank;
        DSU(int n) {
            parent = new int[n];
            rank = new int[n];
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) parent[i] = i;
        }
        int find(int x) {
            if (parent[x] != x) parent[x] = find(parent[x]);
            return parent[x];
        }
        boolean union(int x, int y) {
            int xr = find(x), yr = find(y);
            if (xr == yr) return false;
            if (rank[xr] < rank[yr]) parent[xr] = yr;
            else if (rank[xr] > rank[yr]) parent[yr] = xr;
            else {
                parent[yr] = xr;
                rank[xr]++;
            }
            return true;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int V = sc.nextInt(), E = sc.nextInt();
        Edge[] edges = new Edge[E];
        for (int i = 0; i < E; i++) {
            int u = sc.nextInt(), v = sc.nextInt(), w = sc.nextInt();
            edges[i] = new Edge(u, v, w);
        }
        Arrays.sort(edges);
        DSU dsu = new DSU(V);
        long mstWeight = 0;
        int edgesUsed = 0;
        for (Edge e : edges) {
            if (dsu.union(e.u, e.v)) {
                mstWeight += e.w;
                edgesUsed++;
                if (edgesUsed == V - 1) break;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(mstWeight);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        while (true) {
            int x = sc.nextInt();
            int y = sc.nextInt();
            if (x == 0 && y == 0) break;
            if (x > y) {
                int temp = x;
                x = y;
                y = temp;
            }
            System.out.println(x + " " + y);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int min = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        int max = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
        long sum = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            if (a < min) min = a;
            if (a > max) max = a;
            sum += a;
        }
        System.out.println(min + " " + max + " " + sum);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02411_2P.java: 1-37 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Grading {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        while (true) {
            int m = sc.nextInt();
            int f = sc.nextInt();
            int r = sc.nextInt();
            if (m == -1 && f == -1 && r == -1) break;
            String grade;
            if (m == -1 || f == -1) {
                grade = "F";
            } else {
                int sum = m + f;
                if (sum >= 80) {
                    grade = "A";
                } else if (sum >= 65) {
                    grade = "B";
                } else if (sum >= 50) {
                    grade = "C";
                } else if (sum >= 30) {
                    if (r >= 50) {
                        grade = "C";
                    } else {
                        grade = "D";
                    }
                } else {
                    grade = "F";
                }
            }
            System.out.println(grade);
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02415_0P.java: 1-20 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class ToggleCases {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String input = sc.nextLine();
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        for (char c : input.toCharArray()) {
            if (Character.isUpperCase(c)) {
                sb.append(Character.toLowerCase(c));
            } else if (Character.isLowerCase(c)) {
                sb.append(Character.toUpperCase(c));
            } else {
                sb.append(c);
            }
        }
        System.out.println(sb.toString());
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] A = new int[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        int q = sc.nextInt();
        for (int i = 0; i < q; i++) {
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            int e = sc.nextInt();
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            int count = 0;
            for (int j = b; j < e; j++) {
                if (A[j] == k) count++;
            }
            System.out.println(count);
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02447_3P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    static class Point implements Comparable<Point> {
        int x, y;
        Point(int x, int y) { this.x = x; this.y = y; }
        public int compareTo(Point p) {
            if (this.x != p.x) return Integer.compare(this.x, p.x);
            return Integer.compare(this.y, p.y);
        }
    }
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        Point[] points = new Point[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int x = sc.nextInt(), y = sc.nextInt();
            points[i] = new Point(x, y);
        }
        Arrays.sort(points);
        for (Point p : points) {
            System.out.println(p.x + " " + p.y);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    static class Point implements Comparable<Point> {
        int x, y;
        Point(int x, int y) {
            this.x = x; this.y = y;
        }
        public int compareTo(Point o) {
            if (this.x != o.x) return Integer.compare(this.x, o.x);
            return Integer.compare(this.y, o.y);
        }
    }
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        Point[] points = new Point[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int x = sc.nextInt(), y = sc.nextInt();
            points[i] = new Point(x, y);
        }
        Arrays.sort(points);
        for (Point p : points) {
            System.out.println(p.x + " " + p.y);

    }

train/1/chatgpt_p02467_0P.java: 1-22 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long n = sc.nextLong();
        long originalN = n;
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        sb.append(originalN).append(":");
        for (long i = 2; i * i <= n; i++) {
            while (n % i == 0) {
                sb.append(" ").append(i);
                n /= i;
            }
        }
        if (n > 1) {
            sb.append(" ").append(n);
        }
        System.out.println(sb.toString());
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02469_4P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static long gcd(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long t = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = t;
        }
        return a;
    }

    static long lcm(long a, long b) {
        return a / gcd(a, b) * b;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long res = sc.nextLong();
        for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) {
            long num = sc.nextLong();
            res = lcm(res, num);
        }
        System.out.println(res);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static long gcd(long a, long b) {

            long tmp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = tmp;
        }
        return a;
    }

    static long lcm(long a, long b) {
        return a / gcd(a, b) * b;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long result = sc.nextLong();
        for (int i = 1; i < N; i++) {
            long t = sc.nextLong();

    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static long gcd(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long t = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = t;
        }
        return a;
    }

    static long lcm(long a, long b) {
        return a / gcd(a, b) * b;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long ans = sc.nextLong();
        for (int i = 1; i < N; i++) {
            long t = sc.nextLong();
            ans = lcm(ans, t);
        }
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}

Class 194:   2 fragments, nominal size 25 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p02554_0P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static final int MOD = 1_000_000_007;

    static long modPow(long base, long exp, int mod) {
        long res = 1;
        base %= mod;
        while (exp > 0) {
            if ((exp & 1) == 1) res = res * base % mod;
            base = base * base % mod;
            exp >>= 1;
        }
        return res;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        long total = modPow(10, N, MOD);
        long no0   = modPow(9, N, MOD);
        long no9   = modPow(9, N, MOD);
        long no0no9 = modPow(8, N, MOD);

        long ans = (total - no0 - no9 + no0no9) % MOD;
        if (ans < 0) ans += MOD;
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p02554_1P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static final int MOD = 1_000_000_007;

    static long powmod(long base, long exp, int mod) {
        long result = 1;
        base %= mod;
        while (exp > 0) {
            if ((exp & 1) == 1) result = result * base % mod;
            base = base * base % mod;
            exp >>= 1;
        }
        return result;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        long total = powmod(10, N, MOD);
        long without0 = powmod(9, N, MOD);
        long without9 = powmod(9, N, MOD);
        long without0and9 = powmod(8, N, MOD);

        long ans = (total - without0 - without9 + without0and9) % MOD;
        if (ans < 0) ans += MOD;
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        int rem = 0;
        for (int i = 1; i <= K; i++) {
            rem = (rem * 10 + 7) % K;
            if (rem == 0) {
                System.out.println(i);
                return;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(-1);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02624_0P.java: 1-16 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long ans = 0;
        for (int d = 1; d <= N; d++) {
            int cnt = N / d;
            long sum = (long) d * cnt * (cnt + 1) / 2;
            ans += sum;
        }
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02640_1P.java: 1-19 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int X = sc.nextInt();
        int Y = sc.nextInt();
        boolean found = false;
        for (int cranes = 0; cranes <= X; cranes++) {
            int turtles = X - cranes;
            if (2 * cranes + 4 * turtles == Y) {
                found = true;
                break;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(found ? "Yes" : "No");
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int H1 = sc.nextInt();
        int M1 = sc.nextInt();
        int H2 = sc.nextInt();
        int M2 = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        int start = H1 * 60 + M1;
        int end = H2 * 60 + M2;
        int total = end - start;
        int res = Math.max(0, total - K);
        System.out.println(res);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int H1 = sc.nextInt();
        int M1 = sc.nextInt();
        int H2 = sc.nextInt();
        int M2 = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        int wakeTime = H1 * 60 + M1;
        int sleepTime = H2 * 60 + M2;

        int totalAwakeTime = sleepTime - wakeTime;

        int validPeriod = Math.max(0, totalAwakeTime - K);

        System.out.println(validPeriod);
    }
}

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        boolean[] hasSnack = new boolean[N + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < K; i++) {
            int d = sc.nextInt();
            for (int j = 0; j < d; j++) {
                int snuke = sc.nextInt();
                hasSnack[snuke] = true;
            }
        }

        int count = 0;
        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            if (!hasSnack[i]) count++;
        }
        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long X = sc.nextLong();
        long balance = 100;
        int years = 0;
        while (balance < X) {
            balance = balance + balance / 100;
            years++;
        }
        System.out.println(years);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class SubordinatesCount {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] counts = new int[N + 1];

        for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
            int boss = sc.nextInt();
            counts[boss]++;
        }

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            System.out.println(counts[i]);
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02712_0P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();

        long totalSum = N * (N + 1) / 2;

        long count3 = N / 3;
        long sum3 = 3 * count3 * (count3 + 1) / 2;

        long count5 = N / 5;
        long sum5 = 5 * count5 * (count5 + 1) / 2;

        long count15 = N / 15;
        long sum15 = 15 * count15 * (count15 + 1) / 2;

        long result = totalSum - sum3 - sum5 + sum15;

        System.out.println(result);
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();

        long total = N * (N + 1) / 2;

        long cnt3 = N / 3;
        long sum3 = 3 * cnt3 * (cnt3 + 1) / 2;

        long cnt5 = N / 5;
        long sum5 = 5 * cnt5 * (cnt5 + 1) / 2;

        long cnt15 = N / 15;
        long sum15 = 15 * cnt15 * (cnt15 + 1) / 2;

        long ans = total - sum3 - sum5 + sum15;
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();
        int C = sc.nextInt();

        int temp = A;
        A = B;
        B = temp;

        temp = A;
        A = C;
        C = temp;

        System.out.println(A + " " + B + " " + C);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();

        long cycle = A + B;
        long fullCycles = N / cycle;
        long rem = N % cycle;

        long blue = fullCycles * A + Math.min(rem, A);

        System.out.println(blue);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02754_4P.java: 1-23 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();

        if (A == 0) {
            System.out.println(0);
            return;
        }

        long cycle = A + B;
        long fullCycles = N / cycle;
        long rem = N % cycle;

        long answer = fullCycles * A + Math.min(A, rem);
        System.out.println(answer);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();

        if (A == 0) {
            System.out.println(0);
            return;
        }

        long block = A + B;
        long full_blocks = N / block;
        long rem = N % block;
        long blue = full_blocks * A + Math.min(rem, A);
        System.out.println(blue);
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        String S = sc.next();
        String T = sc.next();
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();
        String U = sc.next();

        if (U.equals(S)) {
            A--;
        } else {
            B--;
        }

        System.out.println(A + " " + B);
    }
}

import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        HashSet<Integer> set = new HashSet<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            if (!set.add(a)) {
                System.out.println("NO");
                return;
            }
        }
        System.out.println("YES");
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02806_4P.java: 1-27 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        String[] titles = new String[N];
        int[] durations = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            titles[i] = sc.next();
            durations[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        String X = sc.next();
        boolean asleep = false;
        int sum = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if (asleep) {
                sum += durations[i];
            }
            if (titles[i].equals(X)) {
                asleep = true;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(sum);
    }
}

        String S = sc.nextLine();

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String S = sc.next();
        int n = S.length();
        int hugs = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n / 2; i++) {
            if (S.charAt(i) != S.charAt(n - 1 - i)) {
                hugs++;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(hugs);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02945_2P.java: 1-17 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();

        int sum = A + B;
        int diff = A - B;
        int prod = A * B;

        int max = Math.max(sum, Math.max(diff, prod));
        System.out.println(max);
    }
}
test/1/claude_p02945_1P.java: 1-17 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();

        int sum = A + B;
        int diff = A - B;
        int product = A * B;

        int max = Math.max(sum, Math.max(diff, product));
        System.out.println(max);
    }

train/1/chatgpt_p02953_0P.java: 1-26 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] H = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            H[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        boolean possible = true;
        for (int i = N - 2; i >= 0; i--) {
            if (H[i] > H[i+1]) {
                H[i]--;
            }
            if (H[i] > H[i+1]) {
                possible = false;
                break;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(possible ? "Yes" : "No");
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02971_4P.java: 1-27 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] A = new int[N];
        int max1 = -1, max2 = -1;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextInt();
            if (A[i] > max1) {
                max2 = max1;
                max1 = A[i];
            } else if (A[i] > max2) {
                max2 = A[i];
            }
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if (A[i] == max1) {
                System.out.println(max2);
            } else {
                System.out.println(max1);
            }
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02983_4P.java: 1-23 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long L = sc.nextLong();
        long R = sc.nextLong();
        int MOD = 2019;
        if (R - L >= MOD) {
            System.out.println(0);
            return;
        }
        int min = MOD;
        for (long i = L; i < R; i++) {
            for (long j = i + 1; j <= R; j++) {
                int val = (int)((i % MOD) * (j % MOD) % MOD);
                if (val < min) min = val;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(min);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long L = sc.nextLong();
        long R = sc.nextLong();
        int mod = 2019;
        if (R - L >= mod) {
            System.out.println(0);
            return;
        }

        int min = mod;
        for (long i = L; i < R; i++) {
            for (long j = i + 1; j <= R; j++) {
                int val = (int)((i % mod) * (j % mod) % mod);
                if (val < min) min = val;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(min);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p02987_2P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String S = sc.next();
        Map<Character, Integer> freq = new HashMap<>();
        for (char c : S.toCharArray()) {
            freq.put(c, freq.getOrDefault(c, 0) + 1);
        }
        if (freq.size() == 2) {
            boolean allTwo = true;
            for (int v : freq.values()) {
                if (v != 2) {
                    allTwo = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            System.out.println(allTwo ? "Yes" : "No");
        } else {
            System.out.println("No");
        }
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long W = sc.nextLong();
        long H = sc.nextLong();
        long x = sc.nextLong();
        long y = sc.nextLong();
        double area = (W * H) / 2.0;
        int multiple = (x * 2 == W && y * 2 == H) ? 1 : 0;
        System.out.printf("%.6f %d\n", area, multiple);
    }

test/1/chatgpt_p03001_0P.java: 1-17 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long W = sc.nextLong();
        long H = sc.nextLong();
        long x = sc.nextLong();
        long y = sc.nextLong();

        double area = (W * H) / 2.0;
        int multi = (x * 2 == W && y * 2 == H) ? 1 : 0;

train/1/chatgpt_p03031_0P.java: 1-40 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        int[] bulbSwitchMask = new int[M];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            int mask = 0;
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                int s = sc.nextInt() - 1;
                mask |= (1 << s);
            }
            bulbSwitchMask[i] = mask;
        }

        int[] p = new int[M];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            p[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int ans = 0;
        for (int sw = 0; sw < (1 << N); sw++) {
            boolean allOn = true;
            for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
                int cnt = Integer.bitCount(sw & bulbSwitchMask[i]);
                if (cnt % 2 != p[i]) {
                    allOn = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (allOn) ans++;
        }
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03031_4P.java: 1-40 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        int[] bulbsMasks = new int[M];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            int mask = 0;
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                int s = sc.nextInt() - 1;
                mask |= (1 << s);
            }
            bulbsMasks[i] = mask;
        }
        int[] p = new int[M];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            p[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int res = 0;
        for (int state = 0; state < (1 << N); state++) {
            boolean ok = true;
            for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
                int onCount = Integer.bitCount(state & bulbsMasks[i]);
                if (onCount % 2 != p[i]) {
                    ok = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (ok) res++;
        }
        System.out.println(res);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03037_1P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        int maxL = 1;
        int minR = N;

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int L = sc.nextInt();
            int R = sc.nextInt();
            if (L > maxL) maxL = L;
            if (R < minR) minR = R;
        }

        int ans = minR - maxL + 1;
        if (ans < 0) ans = 0;
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03037_2P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();
        int left = 1;
        int right = N;

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int L = sc.nextInt();
            int R = sc.nextInt();
            if (L > left) left = L;
            if (R < right) right = R;
        }

        int ans = right - left + 1;
        if (ans < 0) ans = 0;
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class OceanViewInns {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] H = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            H[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int count = 0;
        int maxSoFar = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if (H[i] >= maxSoFar) {
                count++;
                maxSoFar = H[i];
            }
        }
        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String S = sc.next();
        int n = S.length();
        int repaintPattern0 = 0;
        int repaintPattern1 = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            char expected0 = (i % 2 == 0) ? '0' : '1';
            char expected1 = (i % 2 == 0) ? '1' : '0';
            if (S.charAt(i) != expected0) repaintPattern0++;
            if (S.charAt(i) != expected1) repaintPattern1++;
        }
        System.out.println(Math.min(repaintPattern0, repaintPattern1));
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int[] antennas = new int[5];
        for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
            antennas[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        int k = sc.nextInt();

        for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
            for (int j = i + 1; j < 5; j++) {
                if (antennas[j] - antennas[i] > k) {
                    System.out.println(":(");
                    return;
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println("Yay!");
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03089_4P.java: 1-37 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        List<Integer> b = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            b.add(sc.nextInt());
        }

        List<Integer> ops = new ArrayList<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            boolean found = false;
            for (int j = b.size() - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
                if (b.get(j) == j + 1) {
                    ops.add(j + 1);
                    b.remove(j);
                    found = true;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (!found) {
                System.out.println(-1);
                return;
            }
        }

        Collections.reverse(ops);
        for (int op : ops) {
            System.out.println(op);
        }
    }
}

public class Main {

        LinkedList<Integer> b = new LinkedList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            b.add(sc.nextInt());
        }

        ArrayList<Integer> ops = new ArrayList<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            boolean found = false;
            for (int j = b.size() - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
                if (b.get(j) == j + 1) {
                    ops.add(j + 1);
                    b.remove(j);
                    found = true;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (!found) {
                System.out.println(-1);
                return;
            }
        }

        Collections.reverse(ops);

train/1/chatgpt_p03127_3P.java: 1-23 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static long gcd(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long t = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = t;
        }
        return a;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long res = sc.nextLong();
        for (int i = 1; i < N; i++) {
            res = gcd(res, sc.nextLong());
        }
        System.out.println(res);
    }
}

Class 258:   2 fragments, nominal size 25 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p03163_3P.java: 1-33 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int[] w = new int[N];
        int[] v = new int[N];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            w[i] = sc.nextInt();
            v[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        long[] dp = new long[W + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            for (int j = W; j >= w[i]; j--) {
                dp[j] = Math.max(dp[j], dp[j - w[i]] + v[i]);
            }
        }

        long max = 0;
        for (int j = 0; j <= W; j++) {
            if (dp[j] > max) max = dp[j];
        }

        System.out.println(max);
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03163_1P.java: 1-30 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int[] w = new int[N];
        int[] v = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            w[i] = sc.nextInt();
            v[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        long[] dp = new long[W + 1];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            for (int j = W; j >= w[i]; j--) {
                dp[j] = Math.max(dp[j], dp[j - w[i]] + v[i]);
            }
        }

        long ans = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i <= W; i++) {
            if (dp[i] > ans) ans = dp[i];
        }
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}

Class 259:   3 fragments, nominal size 37 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p03165_4P.java: 1-39 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        String t = sc.next();
        int n = s.length();
        int m = t.length();

        int[][] dp = new int[n + 1][m + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {
                if (s.charAt(i) == t.charAt(j)) {
                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] = dp[i][j] + 1;
                } else {
                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] = Math.max(dp[i][j + 1], dp[i + 1][j]);
                }
            }
        }

        StringBuilder lcs = new StringBuilder();
        int i = n, j = m;
        while (i > 0 && j > 0) {
            if (s.charAt(i - 1) == t.charAt(j - 1)) {
                lcs.append(s.charAt(i - 1));
                i--;
                j--;
            } else if (dp[i - 1][j] >= dp[i][j - 1]) {
                i--;
            } else {
                j--;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(lcs.reverse().toString());
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03165_3P.java: 1-39 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        String t = sc.next();
        int n = s.length();
        int m = t.length();
        int[][] dp = new int[n + 1][m + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {
                if (s.charAt(i) == t.charAt(j)) {
                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] = dp[i][j] + 1;
                } else {
                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] = Math.max(dp[i][j + 1], dp[i + 1][j]);
                }
            }
        }

        StringBuilder lcs = new StringBuilder();
        int i = n, j = m;
        while (i > 0 && j > 0) {
            if (s.charAt(i - 1) == t.charAt(j - 1)) {
                lcs.append(s.charAt(i - 1));
                i--;
                j--;
            } else if (dp[i - 1][j] >= dp[i][j - 1]) {
                i--;
            } else {
                j--;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(lcs.reverse().toString());
    }

train/1/chatgpt_p03165_2P.java: 1-40 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        String t = sc.next();
        int n = s.length();
        int m = t.length();

        int[][] dp = new int[n + 1][m + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {
                if (s.charAt(i) == t.charAt(j)) {
                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] = dp[i][j] + 1;
                } else {
                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] = Math.max(dp[i][j + 1], dp[i + 1][j]);
                }
            }
        }

        StringBuilder lcs = new StringBuilder();
        int i = n, j = m;
        while (i > 0 && j > 0) {
            if (s.charAt(i - 1) == t.charAt(j - 1)) {
                lcs.append(s.charAt(i - 1));
                i--;
                j--;
            } else if (dp[i - 1][j] >= dp[i][j - 1]) {
                i--;
            } else {
                j--;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(lcs.reverse().toString());
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03214_2P.java: 1-30 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[N];
        int sum = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
            sum += a[i];
        }

        double avg = (double) sum / N;
        double minDiff = Double.MAX_VALUE;
        int idx = -1;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            double diff = Math.abs(a[i] - avg);
            if (diff < minDiff) {
                minDiff = diff;
                idx = i;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(idx);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class PalaceTemperature {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int T = sc.nextInt();
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int[] H = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            H[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int index = 0;
        double minDiff = Double.MAX_VALUE;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            double temp = T - H[i] * 0.006;
            double diff = Math.abs(temp - A);
            if (diff < minDiff) {
                minDiff = diff;
                index = i;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(index + 1);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03276_0P.java: 1-21 
import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        int[] x = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) x[i] = sc.nextInt();

        int minTime = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        for (int i = 0; i + K - 1 < N; i++) {
            int left = x[i];
            int right = x[i + K - 1];
            int time1 = Math.abs(0 - left) + (right - left);
            int time2 = Math.abs(0 - right) + (right - left);
            minTime = Math.min(minTime, Math.min(time1, time2));
        }
        System.out.println(minTime);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03307_0P.java: 1-23 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    static long gcd(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long t = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = t;
        }
        return a;
    }

    static long lcm(long a, long b) {
        return a / gcd(a, b) * b;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();
        System.out.println(lcm(2, N));
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        List<Integer> coins = new ArrayList<>();
        coins.add(1);
        for (int v = 6; v <= N; v *= 6) coins.add(v);
        for (int v = 9; v <= N; v *= 9) coins.add(v);

        int[] dp = new int[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(dp, Integer.MAX_VALUE);
        dp[0] = 0;

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            for (int c : coins) {
                if (i - c >= 0 && dp[i - c] != Integer.MAX_VALUE) {
                    dp[i] = Math.min(dp[i], dp[i - c] + 1);
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(dp[N]);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03340_0P.java: 1-29 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] A = new int[N];
        for(int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        long ans = 0;
        int right = 0;
        int xor = 0, sum = 0;

        for(int left = 0; left < N; left++) {
            while(right < N && (xor ^ A[right]) == (sum + A[right])) {
                xor ^= A[right];
                sum += A[right];
                right++;
            }
            ans += right - left;
            xor ^= A[left];
            sum -= A[left];
        }
        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03402_0P.java: 1-37 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();

        int h = 100, w = 100;
        char[][] grid = new char[h][w];

        for (int i = 0; i < h / 2; i++) Arrays.fill(grid[i], '#');
        for (int i = h / 2; i < h; i++) Arrays.fill(grid[i], '.');

        int white_needed = A - 1;
        for (int i = 0; i < h / 2 && white_needed > 0; i += 2) {
            for (int j = 0; j < w && white_needed > 0; j += 2) {
                grid[i][j] = '.';
                white_needed--;
            }
        }

        int black_needed = B - 1;
        for (int i = h / 2; i < h && black_needed > 0; i += 2) {
            for (int j = 0; j < w && black_needed > 0; j += 2) {
                grid[i][j] = '#';
                black_needed--;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(h + " " + w);
        for (int i = 0; i < h; i++) {
            System.out.println(new String(grid[i]));
        }
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03404_0P.java: 1-39 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();

        int h = 100, w = 100;
        char[][] grid = new char[h][w];

        for (int i = 0; i < h / 2; i++)
            Arrays.fill(grid[i], '#');
        for (int i = h / 2; i < h; i++)
            Arrays.fill(grid[i], '.');

        int aLeft = A - 1;
        for (int i = 0; i < h / 2 && aLeft > 0; i += 2) {
            for (int j = 0; j < w && aLeft > 0; j += 2) {
                grid[i][j] = '.';
                aLeft--;
            }
        }

        int bLeft = B - 1;
        for (int i = h / 2; i < h && bLeft > 0; i += 2) {
            for (int j = 0; j < w && bLeft > 0; j += 2) {
                grid[i][j] = '#';
                bLeft--;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(h + " " + w);
        for (int i = 0; i < h; i++) {
            System.out.println(new String(grid[i]));
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();
        int count = 0;

        for (int a = 1; a <= 9; a++) {
            for (int b = 0; b <= 9; b++) {
                for (int c = 0; c <= 9; c++) {
                    int palindrome = a * 10000 + b * 1000 + c * 100 + b * 10 + a;
                    if (palindrome >= A && palindrome <= B) {
                        count++;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03434_1P.java: 1-21 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        Integer[] a = new Integer[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        Arrays.sort(a, Collections.reverseOrder());

        int alice = 0, bob = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if (i % 2 == 0) alice += a[i];
            else bob += a[i];
        }
        System.out.println(alice - bob);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03487_0P.java: 1-26 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        Map<Integer, Integer> freq = new HashMap<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int x = sc.nextInt();
            freq.put(x, freq.getOrDefault(x, 0) + 1);
        }
        int removals = 0;
        for (Map.Entry<Integer, Integer> entry : freq.entrySet()) {
            int num = entry.getKey();
            int count = entry.getValue();
            if (count == num) {
            } else if (count > num) {
                removals += (count - num);
            } else {
                removals += count;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(removals);
    }
}

public class GoodSequence {

        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        Map<Integer, Integer> freq = new HashMap<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int x = sc.nextInt();
            freq.put(x, freq.getOrDefault(x, 0) + 1);
        }

        int removeCount = 0;
        for (Map.Entry<Integer, Integer> entry : freq.entrySet()) {
            int num = entry.getKey();
            int count = entry.getValue();
            if (count == num) {
            } else if (count > num) {
                removeCount += (count - num);
            } else {
                removeCount += count;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(removeCount);
    }

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        Map<Integer, Integer> freq = new HashMap<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int x = sc.nextInt();
            freq.put(x, freq.getOrDefault(x, 0) + 1);
        }
        int toRemove = 0;
        for (Map.Entry<Integer, Integer> entry : freq.entrySet()) {
            int num = entry.getKey();
            int cnt = entry.getValue();
            if (cnt == num) continue;
            else if (cnt > num) toRemove += cnt - num;
            else toRemove += cnt;
        }
        System.out.println(toRemove);
    }
}

Class 281:   2 fragments, nominal size 23 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p03495_3P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.*;
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        int[] A = new int[N];
        for(int i = 0; i < N; i++) A[i] = sc.nextInt();

        HashMap<Integer, Integer> freq = new HashMap<>();
        for (int x : A) freq.put(x, freq.getOrDefault(x, 0) + 1);

        if (freq.size() <= K) {
            System.out.println(0);
            return;
        }

        ArrayList<Integer> counts = new ArrayList<>(freq.values());
        Collections.sort(counts);

        int rewrite = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < counts.size() - K; i++) {
            rewrite += counts.get(i);
        }
        System.out.println(rewrite);
    }
}

            System.out.println(0);

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int sum = 0, temp = N;

            sum += temp % 10;
            temp /= 10;
        }
        System.out.println(N % sum == 0 ? "Yes" : "No");
    }

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        if (N == 0) {
            System.out.println(2);
            return;
        }
        if (N == 1) {
            System.out.println(1);
            return;
        }

        long prev2 = 2;
        long prev1 = 1;
        long curr = 0;

        for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
            curr = prev1 + prev2;
            prev2 = prev1;
            prev1 = curr;
        }

        System.out.println(curr);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        if (N == 0) {
            System.out.println(2);
            return;
        }
        if (N == 1) {
            System.out.println(1);
            return;
        }

        long prev2 = 2;
        long prev1 = 1;
        long current = 0;

        for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
            current = prev1 + prev2;
            prev2 = prev1;
            prev1 = current;
        }

        System.out.println(current);
    }
}
