train/1/chatgpt_p03545_3P.java: 1-43 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        int A = s.charAt(0) - '0';
        int B = s.charAt(1) - '0';
        int C = s.charAt(2) - '0';
        int D = s.charAt(3) - '0';

        for (int i = 0; i < 8; i++) {
            int res = A;
            char[] ops = new char[3];
            if ((i & 4) == 0) {
                res += B;
                ops[0] = '+';
            } else {
                res -= B;
                ops[0] = '-';
            }
            if ((i & 2) == 0) {
                res += C;
                ops[1] = '+';
            } else {
                res -= C;
                ops[1] = '-';
            }
            if ((i & 1) == 0) {
                res += D;
                ops[2] = '+';
            } else {
                res -= D;
                ops[2] = '-';
            }
            if (res == 7) {
                System.out.printf("%d%c%d%c%d%c%d=7\n", A, ops[0], B, ops[1], C, ops[2], D);
                break;
            }
        }
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03545_1P.java: 1-26 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();

        int A = s.charAt(0) - '0';
        int B = s.charAt(1) - '0';
        int C = s.charAt(2) - '0';
        int D = s.charAt(3) - '0';

        for (int i = 0; i < 8; i++) {
            int sum = A;
            char[] ops = new char[3];
            if ((i & 4) == 0) { sum += B; ops[0] = '+'; } else { sum -= B; ops[0] = '-'; }
            if ((i & 2) == 0) { sum += C; ops[1] = '+'; } else { sum -= C; ops[1] = '-'; }
            if ((i & 1) == 0) { sum += D; ops[2] = '+'; } else { sum -= D; ops[2] = '-'; }
            if (sum == 7) {
                System.out.printf("%d%c%d%c%d%c%d=7\n", A, ops[0], B, ops[1], C, ops[2], D);
                break;
            }
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03547_4P.java: 1-20 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class HexLetterCompare {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String X = sc.next();
        String Y = sc.next();
        int x = Integer.parseInt(X, 16);
        int y = Integer.parseInt(Y, 16);

        if (x < y) {
            System.out.println("<");
        } else if (x > y) {
            System.out.println(">");
        } else {
            System.out.println("=");
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03583_0P.java: 1-23 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        for (int h = 1; h <= 3500; h++) {
            for (int n = 1; n <= 3500; n++) {
                int denominator = 4 * h * n - N * (h + n);
                if (denominator <= 0) continue;
                int numerator = N * h * n;
                if (numerator % denominator != 0) continue;
                int w = numerator / denominator;
                if (w > 0) {
                    System.out.println(h + " " + n + " " + w);
                    return;
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03592_3P.java: 1-22 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        for (int r = 0; r <= N; r++) {
            for (int c = 0; c <= M; c++) {
                int blacks = r * M + c * N - 2 * r * c;
                if (blacks == K) {
                    System.out.println("Yes");
                    return;
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println("No");
    }
}

Class 290:   2 fragments, nominal size 21 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p03613_1P.java: 1-27 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int MAX_A = 100_000;
        int[] freq = new int[MAX_A + 2];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            freq[a]++;
        }

        int maxCount = 0;
        for (int x = 0; x <= MAX_A; x++) {
            int count = freq[x];
            if (x > 0) count += freq[x - 1];
            if (x < MAX_A) count += freq[x + 1];
            if (count > maxCount) maxCount = count;
        }

        System.out.println(maxCount);
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03611_2P.java: 1-27 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int MAX = 100000;
        int[] cnt = new int[MAX + 2];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            cnt[a]++;
        }

        int ans = 0;
        for (int x = 0; x <= MAX; x++) {
            int sum = cnt[x];
            if (x > 0) sum += cnt[x - 1];
            if (x < MAX) sum += cnt[x + 1];
            if (sum > ans) ans = sum;
        }

        System.out.println(ans);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int x = sc.nextInt();
        int a = sc.nextInt();
        int b = sc.nextInt();

        int distA = (x - a) * (x - a);
        int distB = (x - b) * (x - b);

        System.out.println(distA < distB ? "A" : "B");
    }
}

        int x = scanner.nextInt();
        int a = scanner.nextInt();
        int b = scanner.nextInt();

        int distA = Math.abs(x - a);
        int distB = Math.abs(x - b);

        if (distA < distB) {
            System.out.println("A");
        } else {
            System.out.println("B");
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();
        int C = sc.nextInt();
        int D = sc.nextInt();

        int overlapStart = Math.max(A, C);
        int overlapEnd = Math.min(B, D);

        int result = Math.max(0, overlapEnd - overlapStart);
        System.out.println(result);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03672_0P.java: 1-21 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String S = sc.next();
        int n = S.length();

        for (int len = n - 1; len >= 2; len--) {
            if (len % 2 != 0) continue;
            int half = len / 2;
            String first = S.substring(0, half);
            String second = S.substring(half, len);
            if (first.equals(second)) {
                System.out.println(len);
                return;
            }
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03698_0P.java: 1-19 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class UniqueCharacters {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String S = sc.next();
        boolean[] seen = new boolean[26];
        for (char c : S.toCharArray()) {
            int idx = c - 'a';
            if (seen[idx]) {
                System.out.println("no");
                return;
            }
            seen[idx] = true;
        }
        System.out.println("yes");
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03712_1P.java: 1-23 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class BoxedImage {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int H = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        sc.nextLine();

        String[] image = new String[H];
        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            image[i] = sc.nextLine();
        }

        String border = "#".repeat(W + 2);
        System.out.println(border);
        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            System.out.println("#" + image[i] + "#");
        }
        System.out.println(border);
    }
}

Class 300:   2 fragments, nominal size 25 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p03724_3P.java: 1-30 
import java.io.*;
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        BufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(System.in));
        StringTokenizer st = new StringTokenizer(br.readLine());
        int N = Integer.parseInt(st.nextToken());
        int M = Integer.parseInt(st.nextToken());

        int[] cnt = new int[N + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            st = new StringTokenizer(br.readLine());
            int a = Integer.parseInt(st.nextToken());
            int b = Integer.parseInt(st.nextToken());
            cnt[a] ^= 1;
            cnt[b] ^= 1;
        }

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            if (cnt[i] != 0) {
                System.out.println("NO");
                return;
            }
        }
        System.out.println("YES");
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03738_3P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String A = sc.next();
        String B = sc.next();

        if (A.length() > B.length()) {
            System.out.println("GREATER");
        } else if (A.length() < B.length()) {
            System.out.println("LESS");
        } else {
            int cmp = A.compareTo(B);
            if (cmp > 0) {
                System.out.println("GREATER");

train/1/chatgpt_p03760_1P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String O = sc.nextLine();
        String E = sc.nextLine();
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();

        int lenO = O.length();
        int lenE = E.length();
        int minLen = Math.min(lenO, lenE);

        for (int i = 0; i < minLen; i++) {
            sb.append(O.charAt(i));
            sb.append(E.charAt(i));
        }
        if (lenO > lenE) {
            sb.append(O.charAt(lenO - 1));
        }
        System.out.println(sb.toString());
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String O = sc.nextLine();
        String E = sc.nextLine();

        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        int n = O.length();
        int m = E.length();
        int min = Math.min(n, m);
        for (int i = 0; i < min; i++) {
            sb.append(O.charAt(i));
            sb.append(E.charAt(i));
        }
        if (n > m) {
            sb.append(O.charAt(n - 1));
        }
        System.out.println(sb.toString());
    }
}

Class 306:   2 fragments, nominal size 21 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p03814_1P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        int n = s.length();
        int maxLen = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'A') {
                for (int j = n - 1; j >= i; j--) {
                    if (s.charAt(j) == 'Z') {
                        int len = j - i + 1;
                        if (len > maxLen) maxLen = len;
                        break;
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(maxLen);
    }
}

Class 308:   2 fragments, nominal size 19 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p03829_1P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();

        long[] X = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            X[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long totalFatigue = 0;
        for (int i = 1; i < N; i++) {
            long walkCost = (X[i] - X[i - 1]) * A;
            totalFatigue += Math.min(walkCost, B);
        }
        System.out.println(totalFatigue);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03835_2P.java: 1-20 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        int S = sc.nextInt();
        int count = 0;
        for (int x = 0; x <= K; x++) {
            for (int y = 0; y <= K; y++) {
                int z = S - x - y;
                if (z >= 0 && z <= K) {
                    count++;
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

        if (op.equals("+")) {
            System.out.println(A + B);
        } else {
            System.out.println(A - B);
        }
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03845_4P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] T = new int[N];
        int total = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            T[i] = sc.nextInt();
            total += T[i];
        }

        int M = sc.nextInt();
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int P = sc.nextInt();
            int X = sc.nextInt();
            int newTotal = total - T[P-1] + X;
            System.out.println(newTotal);
        }
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03845_1P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] T = new int[N];
        int baseSum = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            T[i] = sc.nextInt();
            baseSum += T[i];
        }

        int M = sc.nextInt();
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int P = sc.nextInt();
            int X = sc.nextInt();
            int total = baseSum - T[P - 1] + X;
            System.out.println(total);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String S = sc.next();

        int changes = 0;
        char prev = S.charAt(0);
        for (int i = 1; i < S.length(); i++) {
            if (S.charAt(i) != prev) {
                changes++;
                prev = S.charAt(i);
            }
        }
        System.out.println(changes);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03958_1P.java: 1-18 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        int T = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[T];
        int max = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < T; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
            if (a[i] > max) max = a[i];
        }
        int minRepeat = Math.max(0, max - (K - max + 1));
        System.out.println(minRepeat);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p03965_2P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        int N = s.length();

        int atRock = 0;
        int atPaper = 0;
        int score = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            char opp = s.charAt(i);
            if (opp == 'g') {
                if (atPaper + 1 <= atRock) {
                    atPaper++;
                    score++;
                } else {
                    atRock++;
                }
            } else {
                atRock++;
                score--;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(score);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        int n = s.length();

        int rockCount = 0;
        int paperCount = 0;
        int score = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            char opp = s.charAt(i);
            if (opp == 'g') {
                if (rockCount > paperCount) {
                    paperCount++;
                    score++;
                } else {
                    rockCount++;
                }
            } else {
                rockCount++;
                score--;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(score);
    }
}

Class 321:   3 fragments, nominal size 19 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/chatgpt_p03986_0P.java: 1-21 
import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.Deque;
import java.util.ArrayDeque;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String X = sc.next();
        Deque<Character> stack = new ArrayDeque<>();

        for (char c : X.toCharArray()) {
            if (!stack.isEmpty() && stack.peekLast() == 'S' && c == 'T') {
                stack.pollLast();
            } else {
                stack.addLast(c);
            }
        }
        System.out.println(stack.size());
    }
}
test/1/chatgpt_p03986_1P.java: 1-22 
import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.Deque;
import java.util.ArrayDeque;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String X = sc.next();
        Deque<Character> stack = new ArrayDeque<>();

        for (char c : X.toCharArray()) {
            if (!stack.isEmpty() && stack.peek() == 'S' && c == 'T') {
                stack.pop();
            } else {
                stack.push(c);
            }
        }

        System.out.println(stack.size());
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[N + 1];

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int count = 0;

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            int j = a[i];
            if (i < j && a[j] == i) {
                count++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p04011_0P.java: 1-20 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        int X = sc.nextInt();
        int Y = sc.nextInt();

        int firstNights = Math.min(N, K);
        int laterNights = Math.max(0, N - K);

        int total = firstNights * X + laterNights * Y;

        System.out.println(total);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String w = sc.next();
        int[] count = new int[26];
        for (char c : w.toCharArray()) {
            count[c - 'a']++;
        }
        boolean beautiful = true;
        for (int c : count) {
            if (c % 2 != 0) {
                beautiful = false;
                break;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(beautiful ? "Yes" : "No");
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class BeautifulString {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        String w = scanner.nextLine();
        int[] counts = new int[26];

        for (char c : w.toCharArray()) {
            counts[c - 'a']++;
        }

        boolean isBeautiful = true;
        for (int count : counts) {
            if (count % 2 != 0) {
                isBeautiful = false;
                break;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(isBeautiful ? "Yes" : "No");
    }
}

train/1/chatgpt_p04020_3P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long[] A = new long[N + 2];

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long pairs = 0;

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            long pairPrev = Math.min(A[i-1], A[i]);
            pairs += pairPrev;
            A[i-1] -= pairPrev;
            A[i] -= pairPrev;

            long pairNext = Math.min(A[i], A[i+1]);
            pairs += pairNext;
            A[i] -= pairNext;
            A[i+1] -= pairNext;
        }

        System.out.println(pairs);
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long[] A = new long[N + 2];

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long res = 0;
        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            long pair1 = Math.min(A[i - 1], A[i]);
            res += pair1;
            A[i - 1] -= pair1;
            A[i] -= pair1;
            long pair2 = Math.min(A[i], A[i + 1]);
            res += pair2;
            A[i] -= pair2;
            A[i + 1] -= pair2;
        }
        System.out.println(res);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        int n = s.length();

        for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == s.charAt(i + 1)) {
                System.out.println((i + 1) + " " + (i + 2));
                return;
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n - 2; i++) {
            char a = s.charAt(i), b = s.charAt(i + 1), c = s.charAt(i + 2);
            if (a == b || b == c || a == c) {
                System.out.println((i + 1) + " " + (i + 3));
                return;
            }
        }

        System.out.println("-1 -1");
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.Arrays;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = scanner.nextInt();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int[] sides = new int[3];
            sides[0] = scanner.nextInt();
            sides[1] = scanner.nextInt();
            sides[2] = scanner.nextInt();

            Arrays.sort(sides);

            if (sides[0] * sides[0] + sides[1] * sides[1] == sides[2] * sides[2]) {
                System.out.println("YES");
            } else {
                System.out.println("NO");
            }
        }

        scanner.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00005_1P.java: 1-29 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNext()) {
            long a = sc.nextLong();
            long b = sc.nextLong();

            long gcd = gcd(a, b);
            long lcm = (a / gcd) * b;

            System.out.println(gcd + " " + lcm);
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static long gcd(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p00005_4P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        while (sc.hasNextLong()) {
            long a = sc.nextLong();
            long b = sc.nextLong();

            long gcd = calculateGCD(a, b);
            long lcm = (a / gcd) * b;

            System.out.println(gcd + " " + lcm);
        }
        sc.close();
    }

    private static long calculateGCD(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        while (scanner.hasNext()) {
            long a = scanner.nextLong();
            long b = scanner.nextLong();
            long gcd = computeGCD(a, b);
            long lcm = (a / gcd) * b;
            System.out.println(gcd + " " + lcm);
        }
        scanner.close();
    }

    private static long computeGCD(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNext()) {
            long a = sc.nextLong();
            long b = sc.nextLong();

            long gcd = gcd(a, b);
            long lcm = (a / gcd) * b;

            System.out.println(gcd + " " + lcm);
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static long gcd(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00010_2P.java: 1-34 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            double x1 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y1 = sc.nextDouble();
            double x2 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y2 = sc.nextDouble();
            double x3 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y3 = sc.nextDouble();

            double d = 2 * (x1 * (y2 - y3) + x2 * (y3 - y1) + x3 * (y1 - y2));

            double ux = ((x1 * x1 + y1 * y1) * (y2 - y3) +
                        (x2 * x2 + y2 * y2) * (y3 - y1) +
                        (x3 * x3 + y3 * y3) * (y1 - y2)) / d;

            double uy = ((x1 * x1 + y1 * y1) * (x3 - x2) +
                        (x2 * x2 + y2 * y2) * (x1 - x3) +
                        (x3 * x3 + y3 * y3) * (x2 - x1)) / d;

            double r = Math.sqrt((ux - x1) * (ux - x1) + (uy - y1) * (uy - y1));

            System.out.printf("%.3f %.3f %.3f\n", ux, uy, r);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00011_2P.java: 1-32 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int w = sc.nextInt();
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        int[] lines = new int[w + 1];
        for (int i = 1; i <= w; i++) {
            lines[i] = i;
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            String[] parts = sc.next().split(",");
            int a = Integer.parseInt(parts[0]);
            int b = Integer.parseInt(parts[1]);

            int temp = lines[a];
            lines[a] = lines[b];
            lines[b] = temp;
        }

        for (int i = 1; i <= w; i++) {
            System.out.println(lines[i]);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (scanner.hasNextInt()) {
            int d = scanner.nextInt();
            long area = 0;

            for (int x = d; x <= 600 - d; x += d) {
                area += (long) d * x * x;
            }

            System.out.println(area);
        }

        scanner.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00021_4P.java: 1-36 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            double x1 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y1 = sc.nextDouble();
            double x2 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y2 = sc.nextDouble();
            double x3 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y3 = sc.nextDouble();
            double x4 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y4 = sc.nextDouble();

            double abx = x2 - x1;
            double aby = y2 - y1;

            double cdx = x4 - x3;
            double cdy = y4 - y3;

            double cross = abx * cdy - aby * cdx;

            if (Math.abs(cross) < 1e-9) {
                System.out.println("YES");
            } else {
                System.out.println("NO");
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            double x1 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y1 = sc.nextDouble();
            double x2 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y2 = sc.nextDouble();
            double x3 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y3 = sc.nextDouble();
            double x4 = sc.nextDouble();
            double y4 = sc.nextDouble();

            double dx1 = x2 - x1;
            double dy1 = y2 - y1;
            double dx2 = x4 - x3;
            double dy2 = y4 - y3;

            double crossProduct = dx1 * dy2 - dy1 * dx2;

            if (Math.abs(crossProduct) < 1e-9) {
                System.out.println("YES");
            } else {
                System.out.println("NO");
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int[] daysInMonth = {0, 31, 29, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};

        String[] dayNames = {"Thursday", "Friday", "Saturday", "Sunday", "Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday"};

        while (true) {
            int m = sc.nextInt();
            int d = sc.nextInt();

            if (m == 0 && d == 0) break;

            int totalDays = 0;

            for (int i = 1; i < m; i++) {
                totalDays += daysInMonth[i];
            }

            totalDays += d - 1;

            int dayIndex = totalDays % 7;

            System.out.println(dayNames[dayIndex]);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00029_0P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        String text = scanner.nextLine();

        String[] words = text.split(" ");
        Map<String, Integer> frequency = new HashMap<>();

        String longestWord = "";
        for (String word : words) {
            frequency.put(word, frequency.getOrDefault(word, 0) + 1);
            if (word.length() > longestWord.length()) {
                longestWord = word;
            }
        }

        String mostFrequent = "";
        int maxFreq = 0;
        for (Map.Entry<String, Integer> entry : frequency.entrySet()) {
            if (entry.getValue() > maxFreq) {
                maxFreq = entry.getValue();
                mostFrequent = entry.getKey();
            }
        }

        System.out.println(mostFrequent + " " + longestWord);
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class EnglishSentence {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String text = sc.nextLine();
        String[] words = text.split(" ");

        Map<String, Integer> freq = new HashMap<>();
        String maxLenWord = "";
        for (String word : words) {
            freq.put(word, freq.getOrDefault(word, 0) + 1);
            if (word.length() > maxLenWord.length()) {
                maxLenWord = word;
            }
        }

        String mostFreqWord = "";
        int maxFreq = 0;
        for (Map.Entry<String, Integer> entry : freq.entrySet()) {
            if (entry.getValue() > maxFreq) {
                maxFreq = entry.getValue();
                mostFreqWord = entry.getKey();
            }
        }

        System.out.println(mostFreqWord + " " + maxLenWord);
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00031_0P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNextInt()) {
            int weight = sc.nextInt();
            List<Integer> weights = new ArrayList<>();

            for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
                int powerOf2 = 1 << i;
                if ((weight & powerOf2) != 0) {
                    weights.add(powerOf2);
                }
            }

            for (int i = 0; i < weights.size(); i++) {
                if (i > 0) System.out.print(" ");
                System.out.print(weights.get(i));
            }
            System.out.println();
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00032_4P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int rectangles = 0;
        int rhombuses = 0;

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            String[] parts = line.split(",");
            int a = Integer.parseInt(parts[0]);
            int b = Integer.parseInt(parts[1]);
            int c = Integer.parseInt(parts[2]);

            if (a * a + b * b == c * c) {
                rectangles++;
            }
            else if (a == b) {
                rhombuses++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(rectangles);
        System.out.println(rhombuses);
        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        char ballPosition = 'A';

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            String[] positions = line.split(",");
            char pos1 = positions[0].charAt(0);
            char pos2 = positions[1].charAt(0);

            if (ballPosition == pos1) {
                ballPosition = pos2;
            } else if (ballPosition == pos2) {
                ballPosition = pos1;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(ballPosition);
        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNext()) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            int n = sc.nextInt();

            int sum = 0;
            int remainder = a % b;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                remainder *= 10;
                int digit = remainder / b;
                sum += digit;
                remainder = remainder % b;
            }

            System.out.println(sum);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00056_0P.java: 1-36 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        boolean[] isPrime = new boolean[50001];
        Arrays.fill(isPrime, true);
        isPrime[0] = isPrime[1] = false;

        for (int i = 2; i * i <= 50000; i++) {
            if (isPrime[i]) {
                for (int j = i * i; j <= 50000; j += i) {
                    isPrime[j] = false;
                }
            }
        }

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int count = 0;
            for (int i = 2; i <= n / 2; i++) {
                if (isPrime[i] && isPrime[n - i]) {
                    count++;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(count);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}
test/1/claude_p00185_0P.java: 1-36 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        boolean[] isPrime = new boolean[1000001];
        Arrays.fill(isPrime, true);
        isPrime[0] = isPrime[1] = false;

        for (int i = 2; i * i <= 1000000; i++) {
            if (isPrime[i]) {
                for (int j = i * i; j <= 1000000; j += i) {
                    isPrime[j] = false;
                }
            }
        }

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int count = 0;
            for (int p = 2; p <= n / 2; p++) {
                if (isPrime[p] && isPrime[n - p]) {
                    count++;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(count);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}
train/1/claude_p00056_2P.java: 1-36 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        boolean[] isPrime = new boolean[50001];
        Arrays.fill(isPrime, true);
        isPrime[0] = isPrime[1] = false;

        for (int i = 2; i * i <= 50000; i++) {
            if (isPrime[i]) {
                for (int j = i * i; j <= 50000; j += i) {
                    isPrime[j] = false;
                }
            }
        }

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int count = 0;
            for (int i = 2; i <= n / 2; i++) {
                if (isPrime[i] && isPrime[n - i]) {
                    count++;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(count);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00058_0P.java: 1-34 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNext()) {
            double xA = sc.nextDouble();
            double yA = sc.nextDouble();
            double xB = sc.nextDouble();
            double yB = sc.nextDouble();
            double xC = sc.nextDouble();
            double yC = sc.nextDouble();
            double xD = sc.nextDouble();
            double yD = sc.nextDouble();

            double dx1 = xB - xA;
            double dy1 = yB - yA;
            double dx2 = xD - xC;
            double dy2 = yD - yC;

            double dotProduct = dx1 * dx2 + dy1 * dy2;

            if (Math.abs(dotProduct) < 1e-9) {
                System.out.println("YES");
            } else {
                System.out.println("NO");
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class OrthogonalCheck {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (scanner.hasNext()) {
            double xA = scanner.nextDouble();
            double yA = scanner.nextDouble();
            double xB = scanner.nextDouble();
            double yB = scanner.nextDouble();
            double xC = scanner.nextDouble();
            double yC = scanner.nextDouble();
            double xD = scanner.nextDouble();
            double yD = scanner.nextDouble();

            double abX = xB - xA;
            double abY = yB - yA;
            double cdX = xD - xC;
            double cdY = yD - yC;

            double dotProduct = abX * cdX + abY * cdY;

            if (Math.abs(dotProduct) < 1e-10) {
                System.out.println("YES");
            } else {
                System.out.println("NO");
            }
        }
        scanner.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        while (sc.hasNextDouble()) {
            double xa = sc.nextDouble();
            double ya = sc.nextDouble();
            double xb = sc.nextDouble();
            double yb = sc.nextDouble();
            double xc = sc.nextDouble();
            double yc = sc.nextDouble();
            double xd = sc.nextDouble();
            double yd = sc.nextDouble();

            double vABx = xb - xa;
            double vABy = yb - ya;

            double vCDx = xd - xc;
            double vCDy = yd - yc;

            double dotProduct = vABx * vCDx + vABy * vCDy;

            if (Math.abs(dotProduct) < 1e-9) {
                System.out.println("YES");
            } else {
                System.out.println("NO");
            }
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00063_1P.java: 1-34 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        int count = 0;

        while (scanner.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = scanner.nextLine();
            if (isPalindrome(line)) {
                count++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
        scanner.close();
    }

    private static boolean isPalindrome(String str) {
        int left = 0;
        int right = str.length() - 1;

        while (left < right) {
            if (str.charAt(left) != str.charAt(right)) {
                return false;
            }
            left++;
            right--;
        }

        return true;
    }
}

public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int palindromeCount = 0;

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine();
            if (isPalindrome(line)) {
                palindromeCount++;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(palindromeCount);
        sc.close();
    }

    private static boolean isPalindrome(String s) {
        int left = 0;
        int right = s.length() - 1;

        while (left < right) {
            if (s.charAt(left) != s.charAt(right)) {
                return false;
            }
            left++;
            right--;
        }
        return true;
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00064_2P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.regex.Matcher;
import java.util.regex.Pattern;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        int sum = 0;
        Pattern pattern = Pattern.compile("\\d+");

        while (scanner.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = scanner.nextLine();
            Matcher matcher = pattern.matcher(line);

            while (matcher.find()) {
                sum += Integer.parseInt(matcher.group());
            }
        }

        System.out.println(sum);
        scanner.close();
    }
}

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int totalSum = 0;
        Pattern p = Pattern.compile("\\d+");

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine();
            Matcher m = p.matcher(line);
            while (m.find()) {
                totalSum += Integer.parseInt(m.group());
            }
        }
        System.out.println(totalSum);
        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.regex.Matcher;
import java.util.regex.Pattern;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        int sum = 0;
        Pattern pattern = Pattern.compile("\\d+");

        while (scanner.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = scanner.nextLine();
            Matcher matcher = pattern.matcher(line);

            while (matcher.find()) {
                sum += Integer.parseInt(matcher.group());
            }
        }

        System.out.println(sum);
        scanner.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00077_1P.java: 1-36 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (scanner.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = scanner.nextLine();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            StringBuilder result = new StringBuilder();
            int i = 0;

            while (i < line.length()) {
                if (line.charAt(i) == '@') {
                    int count = Character.getNumericValue(line.charAt(i + 1));
                    char ch = line.charAt(i + 2);

                    for (int j = 0; j < count; j++) {
                        result.append(ch);
                    }

                    i += 3;
                } else {
                    result.append(line.charAt(i));
                    i++;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(result.toString());
        }

        scanner.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00079_2P.java: 1-34 
import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.ArrayList;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        ArrayList<Double> x = new ArrayList<>();
        ArrayList<Double> y = new ArrayList<>();

        String line;
        while (scanner.hasNextLine()) {
            line = scanner.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            String[] coords = line.split(",");
            x.add(Double.parseDouble(coords[0]));
            y.add(Double.parseDouble(coords[1]));
        }

        int n = x.size();
        double area = 0.0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int j = (i + 1) % n;
            area += x.get(i) * y.get(j) - x.get(j) * y.get(i);
        }

        area = Math.abs(area) / 2.0;
        System.out.printf("%.6f\n", area);

        scanner.close();
    }
}

        ArrayList<Double> x = new ArrayList<>();
        ArrayList<Double> y = new ArrayList<>();

        String line;
        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            line = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            String[] coords = line.split(",");
            x.add(Double.parseDouble(coords[0]));
            y.add(Double.parseDouble(coords[1]));
        }

        int n = x.size();
        double area = 0.0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int j = (i + 1) % n;
            area += x.get(i) * y.get(j) - x.get(j) * y.get(i);

train/1/claude_p00092_4P.java: 1-38 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            char[][] grid = new char[n][n];
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                grid[i] = sc.next().toCharArray();
            }

            int[][] dp = new int[n][n];
            int maxSize = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                    if (grid[i][j] == '.') {
                        if (i == 0 || j == 0) {
                            dp[i][j] = 1;
                        } else {
                            dp[i][j] = Math.min(dp[i-1][j], Math.min(dp[i][j-1], dp[i-1][j-1])) + 1;
                        }
                        maxSize = Math.max(maxSize, dp[i][j]);
                    }
                }
            }

            System.out.println(maxSize);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00093_1P.java: 1-42 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        boolean first = true;

        while (true) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();

            if (a == 0 && b == 0) break;

            if (!first) {
                System.out.println();
            }
            first = false;

            boolean found = false;
            for (int year = a; year <= b; year++) {
                if (isLeapYear(year)) {
                    System.out.println(year);
                    found = true;
                }
            }

            if (!found) {
                System.out.println("NA");
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static boolean isLeapYear(int year) {
        if (year % 400 == 0) return true;
        if (year % 100 == 0) return false;
        if (year % 4 == 0) return true;
        return false;
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        int maxFish = -1;
        int winnerId = Integer.MAX_VALUE;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int id = sc.nextInt();
            int fish = sc.nextInt();

            if (fish > maxFish || (fish == maxFish && id < winnerId)) {
                maxFish = fish;
                winnerId = id;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(winnerId + " " + maxFish);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00104_1P.java: 1-47 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int H = sc.nextInt();
            int W = sc.nextInt();

            if (H == 0 && W == 0) break;

            char[][] grid = new char[H][W];
            for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
                grid[i] = sc.next().toCharArray();
            }

            Set<String> visited = new HashSet<>();
            int x = 0, y = 0;

            while (true) {
                String pos = x + "," + y;
                if (visited.contains(pos)) {
                    System.out.println("LOOP");
                    break;
                }
                visited.add(pos);

                char tile = grid[y][x];
                if (tile == '.') {
                    System.out.println(x + " " + y);
                    break;
                }

                switch (tile) {
                    case '>': x++; break;
                    case '<': x--; break;
                    case '^': y--; break;
                    case 'v': y++; break;
                }
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

                    System.out.println(x + " " + y);

Class 355:   3 fragments, nominal size 44 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p00110_0P.java: 1-56 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            String result = solve(line);
            System.out.println(result);
        }
        sc.close();
    }

    static String solve(String equation) {
        String[] parts = equation.split("=");
        String leftSide = parts[0];
        String rightSide = parts[1];

        String[] leftParts = leftSide.split("\\+");
        String num1 = leftParts[0];
        String num2 = leftParts[1];
        String result = rightSide;

        for (int x = 0; x <= 9; x++) {
            String testNum1 = num1.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));
            String testNum2 = num2.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));
            String testResult = result.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));

            if (hasLeadingZero(testNum1) || hasLeadingZero(testNum2) || hasLeadingZero(testResult)) {
                continue;
            }

            try {
                long val1 = Long.parseLong(testNum1);
                long val2 = Long.parseLong(testNum2);
                long valResult = Long.parseLong(testResult);

                if (val1 + val2 == valResult) {
                    return String.valueOf(x);
                }
            } catch (NumberFormatException e) {
                continue;
            }
        }

        return "NA";
    }

    static boolean hasLeadingZero(String num) {
        return num.length() > 1 && num.charAt(0) == '0';
    }
}
test/1/claude_p00110_2P.java: 1-56 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            String result = solve(line);
            System.out.println(result);
        }
        sc.close();
    }

    static String solve(String equation) {
        String[] parts = equation.split("=");
        String leftSide = parts[0];
        String rightSide = parts[1];

        String[] addends = leftSide.split("\\+");
        String operand1 = addends[0];
        String operand2 = addends[1];
        String result = rightSide;

        for (int x = 0; x <= 9; x++) {
            String op1 = operand1.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));
            String op2 = operand2.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));
            String res = result.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));

            if (hasLeadingZero(op1) || hasLeadingZero(op2) || hasLeadingZero(res)) {
                continue;
            }

            try {
                long num1 = Long.parseLong(op1);
                long num2 = Long.parseLong(op2);
                long resultNum = Long.parseLong(res);

                if (num1 + num2 == resultNum) {
                    return String.valueOf(x);
                }
            } catch (NumberFormatException e) {
                continue;
            }
        }

        return "NA";
    }

    static boolean hasLeadingZero(String s) {
        return s.length() > 1 && s.charAt(0) == '0';
    }
}
train/1/claude_p00110_1P.java: 1-56 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            String result = solve(line);
            System.out.println(result);
        }
        sc.close();
    }

    static String solve(String equation) {
        String[] parts = equation.split("=");
        String leftSide = parts[0];
        String rightSide = parts[1];

        String[] addends = leftSide.split("\\+");
        String operand1 = addends[0];
        String operand2 = addends[1];
        String result = rightSide;

        for (int x = 0; x <= 9; x++) {
            String op1 = operand1.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));
            String op2 = operand2.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));
            String res = result.replace('X', (char)('0' + x));

            if (hasLeadingZero(op1) || hasLeadingZero(op2) || hasLeadingZero(res)) {
                continue;
            }

            try {
                long num1 = Long.parseLong(op1);
                long num2 = Long.parseLong(op2);
                long sum = Long.parseLong(res);

                if (num1 + num2 == sum) {
                    return String.valueOf(x);
                }
            } catch (NumberFormatException e) {
                continue;
            }
        }

        return "NA";
    }

    static boolean hasLeadingZero(String s) {
        return s.length() > 1 && s.charAt(0) == '0';
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00119_3P.java: 1-48 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int m = sc.nextInt();
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        List<List<Integer>> graph = new ArrayList<>();
        int[] indegree = new int[m + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i <= m; i++) {
            graph.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int x = sc.nextInt();
            int y = sc.nextInt();
            graph.get(x).add(y);
            indegree[y]++;
        }

        Queue<Integer> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        for (int i = 1; i <= m; i++) {
            if (indegree[i] == 0) {
                queue.offer(i);
            }
        }

        List<Integer> result = new ArrayList<>();
        while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
            int curr = queue.poll();
            result.add(curr);

            for (int next : graph.get(curr)) {
                indegree[next]--;
                if (indegree[next] == 0) {
                    queue.offer(next);
                }
            }
        }

        for (int suspect : result) {
            System.out.println(suspect);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        int[] counts = new int[6];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            double height = sc.nextDouble();

            if (height < 165.0) {
                counts[0]++;
            } else if (height < 170.0) {
                counts[1]++;
            } else if (height < 175.0) {
                counts[2]++;
            } else if (height < 180.0) {
                counts[3]++;
            } else if (height < 185.0) {
                counts[4]++;
            } else {
                counts[5]++;
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < 6; i++) {
            System.out.print((i + 1) + ":");
            for (int j = 0; j < counts[i]; j++) {
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int d = sc.nextInt();

        for (int caseNum = 1; caseNum <= d; caseNum++) {
            int s = sc.nextInt();
            System.out.println("Case " + caseNum + ":");

            int current = s;
            for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
                long square = (long) current * current;
                String squareStr = String.format("%08d", square);
                String middle = squareStr.substring(2, 6);
                current = Integer.parseInt(middle);
                System.out.println(current);
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00144_0P.java: 1-66 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        Map<Integer, List<Integer>> graph = new HashMap<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int router = sc.nextInt();
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            List<Integer> connections = new ArrayList<>();
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                connections.add(sc.nextInt());
            }
            graph.put(router, connections);
        }

        int p = sc.nextInt();
        for (int i = 0; i < p; i++) {
            int source = sc.nextInt();
            int dest = sc.nextInt();
            int ttl = sc.nextInt();

            int shortestPath = findShortestPath(graph, source, dest);

            if (shortestPath == -1 || ttl < shortestPath - 1) {
                System.out.println("NA");
            } else {
                System.out.println(shortestPath);
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static int findShortestPath(Map<Integer, List<Integer>> graph, int source, int dest) {
        Queue<Integer> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        Map<Integer, Integer> distance = new HashMap<>();

        queue.offer(source);
        distance.put(source, 1);

        while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
            int current = queue.poll();

            if (current == dest) {
                return distance.get(current);
            }

            List<Integer> neighbors = graph.get(current);
            if (neighbors != null) {
                for (int neighbor : neighbors) {
                    if (!distance.containsKey(neighbor)) {
                        distance.put(neighbor, distance.get(current) + 1);
                        queue.offer(neighbor);
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        return -1;
    }
}
test/1/claude_p00144_4P.java: 1-66 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        Map<Integer, List<Integer>> graph = new HashMap<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int router = sc.nextInt();
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            List<Integer> connections = new ArrayList<>();
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                connections.add(sc.nextInt());
            }
            graph.put(router, connections);
        }

        int p = sc.nextInt();
        for (int i = 0; i < p; i++) {
            int source = sc.nextInt();
            int dest = sc.nextInt();
            int ttl = sc.nextInt();

            int minPath = findShortestPath(graph, source, dest);

            if (minPath == -1 || ttl < minPath - 1) {
                System.out.println("NA");
            } else {
                System.out.println(minPath);
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static int findShortestPath(Map<Integer, List<Integer>> graph, int source, int dest) {
        Queue<Integer> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        Map<Integer, Integer> distances = new HashMap<>();

        queue.offer(source);
        distances.put(source, 1);

        while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
            int current = queue.poll();

            if (current == dest) {
                return distances.get(current);
            }

            List<Integer> neighbors = graph.get(current);
            if (neighbors != null) {
                for (int neighbor : neighbors) {
                    if (!distances.containsKey(neighbor)) {
                        distances.put(neighbor, distances.get(current) + 1);
                        queue.offer(neighbor);
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        return -1;
    }

train/1/claude_p00149_0P.java: 1-46 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int[] leftCount = new int[4];
        int[] rightCount = new int[4];

        while (sc.hasNextLine()) {
            String line = sc.nextLine().trim();
            if (line.isEmpty()) break;

            String[] parts = line.split(" ");
            double left = Double.parseDouble(parts[0]);
            double right = Double.parseDouble(parts[1]);

            if (left >= 1.1) {
                leftCount[0]++;
            } else if (left >= 0.6) {
                leftCount[1]++;
            } else if (left >= 0.2) {
                leftCount[2]++;
            } else {
                leftCount[3]++;
            }

            if (right >= 1.1) {
                rightCount[0]++;
            } else if (right >= 0.6) {
                rightCount[1]++;
            } else if (right >= 0.2) {
                rightCount[2]++;
            } else {
                rightCount[3]++;
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
            System.out.println(leftCount[i] + " " + rightCount[i]);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

Class 362:   2 fragments, nominal size 29 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p00150_3P.java: 1-38 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class TwinPrime {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int maxP = -1, maxQ = -1;

            for (int q = n; q >= 5; q--) {
                if (isPrime(q) && isPrime(q - 2)) {
                    maxP = q - 2;
                    maxQ = q;
                    break;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(maxP + " " + maxQ);
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    static boolean isPrime(int num) {
        if (num < 2) return false;
        if (num == 2) return true;
        if (num % 2 == 0) return false;

        for (int i = 3; i * i <= num; i += 2) {
            if (num % i == 0) return false;
        }
        return true;
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00159_3P.java: 1-35 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int bestId = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
            double minDiff = Double.MAX_VALUE;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int id = sc.nextInt();
                int height = sc.nextInt();
                int weight = sc.nextInt();

                double heightM = height / 100.0;
                double bmi = weight / (heightM * heightM);
                double diff = Math.abs(bmi - 22.0);

                if (diff < minDiff || (diff == minDiff && id < bestId)) {
                    minDiff = diff;
                    bestId = id;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(bestId);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00161_4P.java: 1-46 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static class Team {
        int id;
        int totalSeconds;

        Team(int id, int totalSeconds) {
            this.id = id;
            this.totalSeconds = totalSeconds;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            List<Team> teams = new ArrayList<>();

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int id = sc.nextInt();
                int totalSeconds = 0;

                for (int j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
                    int minutes = sc.nextInt();
                    int seconds = sc.nextInt();
                    totalSeconds += minutes * 60 + seconds;
                }

                teams.add(new Team(id, totalSeconds));
            }

            teams.sort((a, b) -> Integer.compare(a.totalSeconds, b.totalSeconds));

            System.out.println(teams.get(0).id);
            System.out.println(teams.get(1).id);
            System.out.println(teams.get(n-2).id);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00167_0P.java: 1-35 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int[] arr = new int[n];
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                arr[i] = sc.nextInt();
            }

            int swapCount = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {
                for (int j = 0; j < n - 1 - i; j++) {
                    if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1]) {
                        int temp = arr[j];
                        arr[j] = arr[j + 1];
                        arr[j + 1] = temp;
                        swapCount++;
                    }
                }
            }

            System.out.println(swapCount);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

Class 367:   2 fragments, nominal size 51 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p00181_3P.java: 1-63 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int m = sc.nextInt();
            int n = sc.nextInt();

            if (m == 0 && n == 0) break;

            int[] w = new int[n];
            int maxWidth = 0;
            int totalWidth = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                w[i] = sc.nextInt();
                maxWidth = Math.max(maxWidth, w[i]);
                totalWidth += w[i];
            }

            int left = maxWidth;
            int right = totalWidth;
            int answer = right;

            while (left <= right) {
                int mid = left + (right - left) / 2;

                if (canFit(w, m, mid)) {
                    answer = mid;
                    right = mid - 1;
                } else {
                    left = mid + 1;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(answer);
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static boolean canFit(int[] w, int m, int maxWidth) {
        int shelves = 1;
        int currentWidth = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < w.length; i++) {
            if (currentWidth + w[i] <= maxWidth) {
                currentWidth += w[i];
            } else {
                shelves++;
                currentWidth = w[i];
                if (shelves > m) {
                    return false;
                }
            }
        }

        return true;
    }
}
test/1/claude_p00181_4P.java: 1-63 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int m = sc.nextInt();
            int n = sc.nextInt();

            if (m == 0 && n == 0) break;

            int[] w = new int[n];
            int maxWidth = 0;
            int totalWidth = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                w[i] = sc.nextInt();
                maxWidth = Math.max(maxWidth, w[i]);
                totalWidth += w[i];
            }

            int left = maxWidth;
            int right = totalWidth;
            int answer = right;

            while (left <= right) {
                int mid = left + (right - left) / 2;

                if (canFit(w, m, mid)) {
                    answer = mid;
                    right = mid - 1;
                } else {
                    left = mid + 1;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(answer);
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static boolean canFit(int[] w, int m, int maxWidth) {
        int shelves = 1;
        int currentWidth = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < w.length; i++) {
            if (currentWidth + w[i] <= maxWidth) {
                currentWidth += w[i];
            } else {
                shelves++;
                currentWidth = w[i];
                if (shelves > m) {
                    return false;
                }
            }
        }

        return true;
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = scanner.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int[] count = new int[10];

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int type = scanner.nextInt();
                count[type]++;
            }

            for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
                if (count[i] == 0) {
                    System.out.println("-");
                } else {
                    for (int j = 0; j < count[i]; j++) {
                        System.out.print("*");
                    }
                    System.out.println();
                }
            }
        }

        scanner.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int t = sc.nextInt();
            if (t == 0) break;

            int n = sc.nextInt();
            int totalStudyTime = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int start = sc.nextInt();
                int end = sc.nextInt();
                totalStudyTime += (end - start);
            }

            if (totalStudyTime >= t) {
                System.out.println("OK");
            } else {
                System.out.println(t - totalStudyTime);
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

Class 372:   2 fragments, nominal size 31 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p00240_4P.java: 1-40 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            int y = sc.nextInt();

            int bestBank = -1;
            double maxAmount = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                int bankNum = sc.nextInt();
                int rate = sc.nextInt();
                int type = sc.nextInt();

                double amount;
                if (type == 1) {
                    amount = 1 + (rate / 100.0) * y;
                } else {
                    amount = Math.pow(1 + rate / 100.0, y);
                }

                if (amount > maxAmount) {
                    maxAmount = amount;
                    bestBank = bankNum;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(bestBank);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00353_0P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Shopping {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        int m = scanner.nextInt();
        int f = scanner.nextInt();
        int b = scanner.nextInt();

        if (m >= b) {
            System.out.println(0);
        } else {
            int needed = b - m;
            if (needed <= f) {
                System.out.println(needed);
            } else {
                System.out.println("NA");
            }
        }

        scanner.close();
    }
}

Class 380:   4 fragments, nominal size 30 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p00429_0P.java: 1-42 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            String s = sc.next();

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                s = transform(s);
            }

            System.out.println(s);
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static String transform(String s) {
        StringBuilder result = new StringBuilder();
        int i = 0;

        while (i < s.length()) {
            char current = s.charAt(i);
            int count = 1;

            while (i + count < s.length() && s.charAt(i + count) == current) {
                count++;
            }

            result.append(count).append(current);
            i += count;
        }

        return result.toString();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (true) {
            int n = sc.nextInt();
            if (n == 0) break;

            String str = sc.next();

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                str = transform(str);
            }

            System.out.println(str);
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static String transform(String s) {
        StringBuilder result = new StringBuilder();
        int i = 0;

        while (i < s.length()) {
            char current = s.charAt(i);
            int count = 1;

            while (i + count < s.length() && s.charAt(i + count) == current) {
                count++;
            }

            result.append(count).append(current);
            i += count;
        }

        return result.toString();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        String input = scanner.nextLine();

        StringBuilder result = new StringBuilder();
        for (char c : input.toCharArray()) {
            char decoded = (char) ((c - 'A' - 3 + 26) % 26 + 'A');
            result.append(decoded);
        }

        System.out.println(result.toString());
    }
}

Class 382:   8 fragments, nominal size 23 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p00445_0P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        while (sc.hasNext()) {
            String s = sc.next();
            int joiCount = 0;
            int ioiCount = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i <= s.length() - 3; i++) {
                String sub = s.substring(i, i + 3);
                if (sub.equals("JOI")) {
                    joiCount++;
                } else if (sub.equals("IOI")) {
                    ioiCount++;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(joiCount);
            System.out.println(ioiCount);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

            for (int i = 0; i <= s.length() - 3; i++) {
                String sub = s.substring(i, i + 3);
                if (sub.equals("JOI")) {
                    joiCount++;
                } else if (sub.equals("IOI")) {
                    ioiCount++;
                }
            }

            System.out.println(joiCount);
            System.out.println(ioiCount);
        }
        scanner.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);

        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            int startH = scanner.nextInt();
            int startM = scanner.nextInt();
            int startS = scanner.nextInt();
            int endH = scanner.nextInt();
            int endM = scanner.nextInt();
            int endS = scanner.nextInt();

            int startSeconds = startH * 3600 + startM * 60 + startS;
            int endSeconds = endH * 3600 + endM * 60 + endS;

            int workSeconds = endSeconds - startSeconds;

            int hours = workSeconds / 3600;
            int minutes = (workSeconds % 3600) / 60;
            int seconds = workSeconds % 60;

            System.out.println(hours + " " + minutes + " " + seconds);
        }

        scanner.close();
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            int h1 = sc.nextInt();
            int m1 = sc.nextInt();
            int s1 = sc.nextInt();
            int h2 = sc.nextInt();
            int m2 = sc.nextInt();
            int s2 = sc.nextInt();

            int start = h1 * 3600 + m1 * 60 + s1;
            int end = h2 * 3600 + m2 * 60 + s2;

            int diff = end - start;

            int hours = diff / 3600;
            int minutes = (diff % 3600) / 60;
            int seconds = diff % 60;

            System.out.println(hours + " " + minutes + " " + seconds);
        }

        sc.close();
    }

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            int inH = sc.nextInt();
            int inM = sc.nextInt();
            int inS = sc.nextInt();
            int outH = sc.nextInt();
            int outM = sc.nextInt();
            int outS = sc.nextInt();

            int totalSecondsIn = inH * 3600 + inM * 60 + inS;
            int totalSecondsOut = outH * 3600 + outM * 60 + outS;

            int durationSeconds = totalSecondsOut - totalSecondsIn;

            int h = durationSeconds / 3600;
            int m = (durationSeconds % 3600) / 60;
            int s = durationSeconds % 60;

            System.out.println(h + " " + m + " " + s);
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int[] wScores = new int[10];
        for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
            wScores[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int[] kScores = new int[10];
        for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
            kScores[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        Arrays.sort(wScores);
        Arrays.sort(kScores);

        int wTotal = wScores[9] + wScores[8] + wScores[7];
        int kTotal = kScores[9] + kScores[8] + kScores[7];

        System.out.println(wTotal + " " + kTotal);

        sc.close();
    }
}
