train/1/claude_p02564_3P.java: 1-77 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static List<List<Integer>> adj, radj;
    static boolean[] visited;
    static Stack<Integer> finishOrder;
    static List<List<Integer>> sccs;

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int m = sc.nextInt();

        adj = new ArrayList<>();
        radj = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            adj.add(new ArrayList<>());
            radj.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            adj.get(a).add(b);
            radj.get(b).add(a);
        }

        visited = new boolean[n];
        finishOrder = new Stack<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (!visited[i]) {
                dfs1(i);
            }
        }

        visited = new boolean[n];
        sccs = new ArrayList<>();
        while (!finishOrder.isEmpty()) {
            int v = finishOrder.pop();
            if (!visited[v]) {
                List<Integer> scc = new ArrayList<>();
                dfs2(v, scc);
                sccs.add(scc);
            }
        }

        System.out.println(sccs.size());
        for (List<Integer> scc : sccs) {
            System.out.print(scc.size());
            for (int v : scc) {
                System.out.print(" " + v);
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }

    static void dfs1(int v) {
        visited[v] = true;
        for (int u : adj.get(v)) {
            if (!visited[u]) {
                dfs1(u);
            }
        }
        finishOrder.push(v);
    }

    static void dfs2(int v, List<Integer> scc) {
        visited[v] = true;
        scc.add(v);
        for (int u : radj.get(v)) {
            if (!visited[u]) {
                dfs2(u, scc);
            }
        }
    }
}
test/1/claude_p02564_2P.java: 1-77 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static List<List<Integer>> graph, transpose;
    static boolean[] visited;
    static Stack<Integer> finishOrder;
    static List<List<Integer>> sccs;

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int m = sc.nextInt();

        graph = new ArrayList<>();
        transpose = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            graph.add(new ArrayList<>());
            transpose.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            graph.get(a).add(b);
            transpose.get(b).add(a);
        }

        visited = new boolean[n];
        finishOrder = new Stack<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (!visited[i]) {
                dfs1(i);
            }
        }

        visited = new boolean[n];
        sccs = new ArrayList<>();
        while (!finishOrder.isEmpty()) {
            int v = finishOrder.pop();
            if (!visited[v]) {
                List<Integer> scc = new ArrayList<>();
                dfs2(v, scc);
                sccs.add(scc);
            }
        }

        System.out.println(sccs.size());
        for (List<Integer> scc : sccs) {
            System.out.print(scc.size());
            for (int v : scc) {
                System.out.print(" " + v);
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }

    static void dfs1(int v) {
        visited[v] = true;
        for (int u : graph.get(v)) {
            if (!visited[u]) {
                dfs1(u);
            }
        }
        finishOrder.push(v);
    }

    static void dfs2(int v, List<Integer> scc) {
        visited[v] = true;
        scc.add(v);
        for (int u : transpose.get(v)) {
            if (!visited[u]) {
                dfs2(u, scc);
            }
        }
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long[] a = new long[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long MOD = 1000000007;
        long result = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {
            for (int j = i + 1; j < n; j++) {
                result = (result + (a[i] * a[j]) % MOD) % MOD;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(result);
    }

train/1/claude_p02596_4P.java: 1-30 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        Set<Integer> seen = new HashSet<>();
        int remainder = 0;
        int position = 0;

        while (true) {
            remainder = (remainder * 10 + 7) % K;
            position++;

            if (remainder == 0) {
                System.out.println(position);
                return;
            }

            if (seen.contains(remainder)) {
                System.out.println(-1);
                return;
            }

            seen.add(remainder);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        long[] A = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        for (int i = K; i < N; i++) {
            if (A[i] > A[i - K]) {
                System.out.println("Yes");
            } else {
                System.out.println("No");
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

        counts.put("AC", 0);
        counts.put("WA", 0);
        counts.put("TLE", 0);
        counts.put("RE", 0);

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            String verdict = sc.next();
            counts.put(verdict, counts.get(verdict) + 1);
        }

        System.out.println("AC x " + counts.get("AC"));
        System.out.println("WA x " + counts.get("WA"));
        System.out.println("TLE x " + counts.get("TLE"));
        System.out.println("RE x " + counts.get("RE"));
    }

train/1/claude_p02614_2P.java: 1-43 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int H = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        char[][] grid = new char[H][W];
        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            grid[i] = sc.next().toCharArray();
        }

        int count = 0;

        for (int rowMask = 0; rowMask < (1 << H); rowMask++) {
            for (int colMask = 0; colMask < (1 << W); colMask++) {
                int blackRemaining = 0;

                for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
                    for (int j = 0; j < W; j++) {
                        if (grid[i][j] == '#') {
                            boolean rowSelected = (rowMask & (1 << i)) != 0;
                            boolean colSelected = (colMask & (1 << j)) != 0;

                            if (!rowSelected && !colSelected) {
                                blackRemaining++;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }

                if (blackRemaining == K) {
                    count++;
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02631_2P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int s = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            s ^= a[i];
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (i > 0) System.out.print(" ");
            System.out.print(s ^ a[i]);
        }
        System.out.println();
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int count = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            boolean hasDevisor = false;

            for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                if (i != j && a[i] % a[j] == 0) {
                    hasDevisor = true;
                    break;
                }
            }

            if (!hasDevisor) {
                count++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

Class 469:   4 fragments, nominal size 57 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p02678_3P.java: 1-65 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        List<List<Integer>> graph = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i <= N; i++) {
            graph.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            graph.get(a).add(b);
            graph.get(b).add(a);
        }

        int[] dist = new int[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(dist, -1);
        Queue<Integer> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        queue.offer(1);
        dist[1] = 0;

        while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
            int curr = queue.poll();
            for (int next : graph.get(curr)) {
                if (dist[next] == -1) {
                    dist[next] = dist[curr] + 1;
                    queue.offer(next);
                }
            }
        }

        int[] signpost = new int[N + 1];
        boolean possible = true;

        for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
            boolean found = false;
            for (int neighbor : graph.get(i)) {
                if (dist[neighbor] == dist[i] - 1) {
                    signpost[i] = neighbor;
                    found = true;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (!found) {
                possible = false;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (!possible) {
            System.out.println("No");
        } else {
            System.out.println("Yes");
            for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
                System.out.println(signpost[i]);
            }
        }
    }
}
test/1/claude_p02678_4P.java: 1-65 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int m = sc.nextInt();

        List<List<Integer>> graph = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i <= n; i++) {
            graph.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            graph.get(a).add(b);
            graph.get(b).add(a);
        }

        int[] dist = new int[n + 1];
        Arrays.fill(dist, -1);
        Queue<Integer> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        queue.offer(1);
        dist[1] = 0;

        while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
            int curr = queue.poll();
            for (int next : graph.get(curr)) {
                if (dist[next] == -1) {
                    dist[next] = dist[curr] + 1;
                    queue.offer(next);
                }
            }
        }

        int[] signpost = new int[n + 1];
        boolean possible = true;

        for (int i = 2; i <= n; i++) {
            boolean found = false;
            for (int neighbor : graph.get(i)) {
                if (dist[neighbor] == dist[i] - 1) {
                    signpost[i] = neighbor;
                    found = true;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (!found) {
                possible = false;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (!possible) {
            System.out.println("No");
        } else {
            System.out.println("Yes");
            for (int i = 2; i <= n; i++) {
                System.out.println(signpost[i]);

train/1/claude_p02678_0P.java: 1-65 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        List<List<Integer>> graph = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i <= N; i++) {
            graph.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            graph.get(a).add(b);
            graph.get(b).add(a);
        }

        int[] dist = new int[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(dist, -1);
        Queue<Integer> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        queue.offer(1);
        dist[1] = 0;

        while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
            int curr = queue.poll();
            for (int next : graph.get(curr)) {
                if (dist[next] == -1) {
                    dist[next] = dist[curr] + 1;
                    queue.offer(next);
                }
            }
        }

        int[] signpost = new int[N + 1];
        boolean possible = true;

        for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
            boolean found = false;
            for (int neighbor : graph.get(i)) {
                if (dist[neighbor] == dist[i] - 1) {
                    signpost[i] = neighbor;
                    found = true;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (!found) {
                possible = false;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (!possible) {
            System.out.println("No");
        } else {
            System.out.println("Yes");
            for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
                System.out.println(signpost[i]);
            }
        }
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02684_0P.java: 1-38 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long K = sc.nextLong();

        int[] A = new int[N + 1];
        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        Map<Integer, Integer> visited = new HashMap<>();
        List<Integer> path = new ArrayList<>();

        int current = 1;
        int step = 0;

        while (!visited.containsKey(current)) {
            visited.put(current, step);
            path.add(current);
            current = A[current];
            step++;
        }

        int cycleStart = visited.get(current);
        int cycleLength = step - cycleStart;

        if (K < cycleStart) {
            System.out.println(path.get((int)K));
        } else {
            long remaining = (K - cycleStart) % cycleLength;
            System.out.println(path.get((int)(cycleStart + remaining)));
        }
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        int[] H = new int[N + 1];
        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            H[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        List<List<Integer>> adj = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i <= N; i++) {
            adj.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            adj.get(a).add(b);
            adj.get(b).add(a);
        }

        int goodCount = 0;
        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            boolean isGood = true;
            for (int neighbor : adj.get(i)) {
                if (H[i] <= H[neighbor]) {
                    isGood = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (isGood) {
                goodCount++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(goodCount);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();
        int C = sc.nextInt();
        int D = sc.nextInt();

        int takahashiTurns = (C + B - 1) / B;
        int aokiTurns = (A + D - 1) / D;

        if (takahashiTurns <= aokiTurns) {
            System.out.println("Yes");
        } else {
            System.out.println("No");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02709_1P.java: 1-30 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long[] a = new long[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long[] dp = new long[1 << n];

        for (int mask = 0; mask < (1 << n); mask++) {
            int pos = Integer.bitCount(mask);
            if (pos == n) continue;

            for (int orig = 0; orig < n; orig++) {
                if ((mask & (1 << orig)) == 0) {
                    int newMask = mask | (1 << orig);
                    long happiness = a[orig] * Math.abs(orig - pos);
                    dp[newMask] = Math.max(dp[newMask], dp[mask] + happiness);
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(dp[(1 << n) - 1]);
    }
}
test/1/claude_p02709_0P.java: 1-30 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long[] a = new long[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long[] dp = new long[1 << n];

        for (int mask = 0; mask < (1 << n); mask++) {
            int pos = Integer.bitCount(mask);
            if (pos == n) continue;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                if ((mask & (1 << i)) == 0) {
                    int newMask = mask | (1 << i);
                    long happiness = a[i] * Math.abs(i - pos);
                    dp[newMask] = Math.max(dp[newMask], dp[mask] + happiness);
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(dp[(1 << n) - 1]);
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02713_0P.java: 1-29 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        long sum = 0;
        for (int a = 1; a <= K; a++) {
            for (int b = 1; b <= K; b++) {
                for (int c = 1; c <= K; c++) {
                    sum += gcd(gcd(a, b), c);
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(sum);
    }

    private static int gcd(int a, int b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            int temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        String S = sc.next();

        int count = 0;

        for (int j = 1; j < N - 1; j++) {
            for (int i = 0; i < j; i++) {
                for (int k = j + 1; k < N; k++) {
                    if (S.charAt(i) != S.charAt(j) &&
                        S.charAt(i) != S.charAt(k) &&
                        S.charAt(j) != S.charAt(k)) {

                        if ((j - i) != (k - j)) {
                            count++;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02721_0P.java: 1-47 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        int C = sc.nextInt();
        String S = sc.next();

        List<Integer> earliest = new ArrayList<>();
        int pos = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < K; i++) {
            while (pos < N && S.charAt(pos) == 'x') {
                pos++;
            }
            earliest.add(pos + 1);
            pos += C + 1;
        }

        List<Integer> latest = new ArrayList<>();
        pos = N - 1;
        for (int i = 0; i < K; i++) {
            while (pos >= 0 && S.charAt(pos) == 'x') {
                pos--;
            }
            latest.add(pos + 1);
            pos -= C + 1;
        }
        Collections.reverse(latest);

        Set<Integer> result = new HashSet<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < K; i++) {
            if (earliest.get(i).equals(latest.get(i))) {
                result.add(earliest.get(i));
            }
        }

        List<Integer> answer = new ArrayList<>(result);
        Collections.sort(answer);

        for (int day : answer) {
            System.out.println(day);
        }
    }
}

            while (pos < N && S.charAt(pos) == 'x') {
                pos++;
            }
            earliest.add(pos + 1);
            pos += C + 1;
        }

        List<Integer> latest = new ArrayList<>();
        pos = N - 1;
        for (int i = 0; i < K; i++) {
            while (pos >= 0 && S.charAt(pos) == 'x') {
                pos--;
            }
            latest.add(pos + 1);
            pos -= C + 1;

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();

        long cycleLength = A + B;
        long completeCycles = N / cycleLength;
        long remainder = N % cycleLength;

        long blueBalls = completeCycles * A;

        if (remainder > 0) {
            blueBalls += Math.min(remainder, A);
        }

        System.out.println(blueBalls);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();

        double min1 = A / 0.08;
        double max1 = (A + 1) / 0.08;

        double min2 = B / 0.10;
        double max2 = (B + 1) / 0.10;

        double minP = Math.max(min1, min2);
        double maxP = Math.min(max1, max2);

        if (minP >= maxP) {
            System.out.println(-1);
            return;
        }

        int candidate = (int) Math.ceil(minP);

        if (candidate < maxP &&
            (int)(candidate * 0.08) == A &&
            (int)(candidate * 0.10) == B) {
            System.out.println(candidate);
        } else {
            System.out.println(-1);
        }
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02760_3P.java: 1-59 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int[][] grid = new int[3][3];
        boolean[][] marked = new boolean[3][3];

        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
                grid[i][j] = sc.nextInt();
            }
        }

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        Set<Integer> calledNumbers = new HashSet<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            calledNumbers.add(sc.nextInt());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
                if (calledNumbers.contains(grid[i][j])) {
                    marked[i][j] = true;
                }
            }
        }

        boolean bingo = false;

        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            if (marked[i][0] && marked[i][1] && marked[i][2]) {
                bingo = true;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (!bingo) {
            for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
                if (marked[0][j] && marked[1][j] && marked[2][j]) {
                    bingo = true;
                    break;
                }
            }
        }

        if (!bingo) {
            if ((marked[0][0] && marked[1][1] && marked[2][2]) ||
                (marked[0][2] && marked[1][1] && marked[2][0])) {
                bingo = true;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(bingo ? "Yes" : "No");
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int[][] grid = new int[3][3];
        boolean[][] marked = new boolean[3][3];

        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
                grid[i][j] = sc.nextInt();
            }
        }

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        Set<Integer> chosenNumbers = new HashSet<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            chosenNumbers.add(sc.nextInt());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
                if (chosenNumbers.contains(grid[i][j])) {
                    marked[i][j] = true;
                }
            }
        }

        boolean hasBingo = false;

        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
            if (marked[i][0] && marked[i][1] && marked[i][2]) {
                hasBingo = true;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (!hasBingo) {
            for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
                if (marked[0][j] && marked[1][j] && marked[2][j]) {
                    hasBingo = true;
                    break;
                }
            }
        }

        if (!hasBingo) {
            if ((marked[0][0] && marked[1][1] && marked[2][2]) ||

                hasBingo = true;

train/1/claude_p02773_2P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        Map<String, Integer> count = new HashMap<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            String s = sc.next();
            count.put(s, count.getOrDefault(s, 0) + 1);
        }

        int maxCount = Collections.max(count.values());

        List<String> result = new ArrayList<>();
        for (Map.Entry<String, Integer> entry : count.entrySet()) {
            if (entry.getValue() == maxCount) {
                result.add(entry.getKey());
            }
        }

        Collections.sort(result);

        for (String s : result) {
            System.out.println(s);
        }
    }
}

        }

        List<String> result = new ArrayList<>();
        for (Map.Entry<String, Integer> entry : count.entrySet()) {
            if (entry.getValue() == maxCount) {
                result.add(entry.getKey());
            }
        }

        Collections.sort(result);

        for (String s : result) {
            System.out.println(s);
        }
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02795_0P.java: 1-24 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int H = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        int minOps = Integer.MAX_VALUE;

        for (int r = 0; r <= H; r++) {
            for (int c = 0; c <= W; c++) {
                int blackSquares = r * W + c * H - r * c;
                if (blackSquares >= N) {
                    minOps = Math.min(minOps, r + c);
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(minOps);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();
        long K = sc.nextLong();

        if (K <= A) {
            System.out.println((A - K) + " " + B);
        } else {
            long remaining = K - A;
            long aokiLeft = Math.max(0, B - remaining);
            System.out.println("0 " + aokiLeft);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int expected = 1;
        int kept = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (a[i] == expected) {
                expected++;
                kept++;
            }
        }

        if (kept == 0) {
            System.out.println(-1);
        } else {
            System.out.println(n - kept);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        String s = sc.next();

        Set<String> pinCodes = new HashSet<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n - 2; i++) {
            for (int j = i + 1; j < n - 1; j++) {
                for (int k = j + 1; k < n; k++) {
                    String pin = "" + s.charAt(i) + s.charAt(j) + s.charAt(k);
                    pinCodes.add(pin);
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(pinCodes.size());
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02845_0P.java: 1-55 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static final int MOD = 1000000007;

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        Map<String, Long> dp = new HashMap<>();
        dp.put("0,0,0", 1L);

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            Map<String, Long> newDp = new HashMap<>();

            for (String state : dp.keySet()) {
                String[] parts = state.split(",");
                int r = Integer.parseInt(parts[0]);
                int g = Integer.parseInt(parts[1]);
                int b = Integer.parseInt(parts[2]);

                long ways = dp.get(state);

                if (r == a[i]) {
                    String newState = (r + 1) + "," + g + "," + b;
                    newDp.put(newState, (newDp.getOrDefault(newState, 0L) + ways) % MOD);
                }

                if (g == a[i]) {
                    String newState = r + "," + (g + 1) + "," + b;
                    newDp.put(newState, (newDp.getOrDefault(newState, 0L) + ways) % MOD);
                }

                if (b == a[i]) {
                    String newState = r + "," + g + "," + (b + 1);
                    newDp.put(newState, (newDp.getOrDefault(newState, 0L) + ways) % MOD);
                }
            }

            dp = newDp;
        }

        long result = 0;
        for (long ways : dp.values()) {
            result = (result + ways) % MOD;
        }

        System.out.println(result);
    }
}
test/1/claude_p02845_4P.java: 1-55 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static final int MOD = 1000000007;

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        Map<String, Long> dp = new HashMap<>();
        dp.put("0,0,0", 1L);

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            Map<String, Long> nextDp = new HashMap<>();

            for (String state : dp.keySet()) {
                String[] parts = state.split(",");
                int r = Integer.parseInt(parts[0]);
                int b = Integer.parseInt(parts[1]);
                int g = Integer.parseInt(parts[2]);

                long ways = dp.get(state);

                if (r == a[i]) {
                    String nextState = (r+1) + "," + b + "," + g;
                    nextDp.put(nextState, (nextDp.getOrDefault(nextState, 0L) + ways) % MOD);
                }

                if (b == a[i]) {
                    String nextState = r + "," + (b+1) + "," + g;
                    nextDp.put(nextState, (nextDp.getOrDefault(nextState, 0L) + ways) % MOD);
                }

                if (g == a[i]) {
                    String nextState = r + "," + b + "," + (g+1);
                    nextDp.put(nextState, (nextDp.getOrDefault(nextState, 0L) + ways) % MOD);
                }
            }

            dp = nextDp;
        }

        long result = 0;
        for (long ways : dp.values()) {
            result = (result + ways) % MOD;
        }

        System.out.println(result);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        String S = sc.next();

        if (N % 2 == 1) {
            System.out.println("No");
        } else {
            String firstHalf = S.substring(0, N / 2);
            String secondHalf = S.substring(N / 2);

            if (firstHalf.equals(secondHalf)) {
                System.out.println("Yes");
            } else {
                System.out.println("No");
            }
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();

        long minMoves = Long.MAX_VALUE;

        for (long i = 1; i * i <= N; i++) {
            if (N % i == 0) {
                long j = N / i;
                long moves = i + j - 2;
                minMoves = Math.min(minMoves, moves);
            }
        }

        System.out.println(minMoves);
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        Map<Integer, Integer> freq = new HashMap<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            freq.put(a, freq.getOrDefault(a, 0) + 1);
        }

        List<Integer> frequencies = new ArrayList<>(freq.values());
        Collections.sort(frequencies, Collections.reverseOrder());

        for (int k = 1; k <= n; k++) {
            if (k > frequencies.size()) {
                System.out.println(0);
            } else {
                System.out.println(frequencies.get(k - 1));
            }
        }
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02904_2P.java: 1-30 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int k = sc.nextInt();
        int[] p = new int[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            p[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        Set<String> results = new HashSet<>();

        for (int start = 0; start <= n - k; start++) {
            int[] temp = p.clone();

            Arrays.sort(temp, start, start + k);

            StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                sb.append(temp[i]).append(",");
            }
            results.add(sb.toString());
        }

        System.out.println(results.size());
    }
}

Class 505:   2 fragments, nominal size 32 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p02914_3P.java: 1-40 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long[] a = new long[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long totalXor = 0;
        for (long x : a) {
            totalXor ^= x;
        }

        Set<Long> possibleXors = new HashSet<>();

        for (int mask = 1; mask < (1 << n) - 1; mask++) {
            long xor = 0;
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                if ((mask & (1 << i)) != 0) {
                    xor ^= a[i];
                }
            }
            possibleXors.add(xor);
        }

        long maxBeauty = 0;
        for (long redXor : possibleXors) {
            long blueXor = totalXor ^ redXor;
            long beauty = redXor + blueXor;
            maxBeauty = Math.max(maxBeauty, beauty);
        }

        System.out.println(maxBeauty);
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long[] a = new long[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long totalXor = 0;
        for (long x : a) {
            totalXor ^= x;
        }

        Set<Long> possibleXors = new HashSet<>();

        for (int mask = 1; mask < (1 << n) - 1; mask++) {
            long xor = 0;
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                if ((mask & (1 << i)) != 0) {
                    xor ^= a[i];
                }
            }
            possibleXors.add(xor);
        }

        long maxBeauty = 0;
        for (long redXor : possibleXors) {
            long blueXor = redXor ^ totalXor;
            long beauty = redXor + blueXor;
            maxBeauty = Math.max(maxBeauty, beauty);

        System.out.println(maxBeauty);

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] b = new int[n-1];

        for (int i = 0; i < n-1; i++) {
            b[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int sum = 0;

        sum += b[0];

        for (int i = 1; i < n-1; i++) {
            sum += Math.min(b[i-1], b[i]);
        }

        sum += b[n-2];

        System.out.println(sum);
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        Map<String, Integer> anagramGroups = new HashMap<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            String s = sc.next();
            char[] chars = s.toCharArray();
            Arrays.sort(chars);
            String sorted = new String(chars);

            anagramGroups.put(sorted, anagramGroups.getOrDefault(sorted, 0) + 1);
        }

        long result = 0;
        for (int count : anagramGroups.values()) {
            if (count > 1) {
                result += (long) count * (count - 1) / 2;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(result);
    }
}

Class 510:   2 fragments, nominal size 63 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p02949_0P.java: 1-70 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static class Edge {
        int to, cost;
        Edge(int to, int cost) {
            this.to = to;
            this.cost = cost;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();
        int P = sc.nextInt();

        List<Edge>[] graph = new List[N + 1];
        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            graph[i] = new ArrayList<>();
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            int c = sc.nextInt();
            graph[a].add(new Edge(b, P - c));
        }

        long[] dist = new long[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(dist, Long.MAX_VALUE);
        dist[1] = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < N - 1; i++) {
            for (int u = 1; u <= N; u++) {
                if (dist[u] == Long.MAX_VALUE) continue;
                for (Edge e : graph[u]) {
                    if (dist[u] + e.cost < dist[e.to]) {
                        dist[e.to] = dist[u] + e.cost;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        boolean[] hasPosCycle = new boolean[N + 1];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            for (int u = 1; u <= N; u++) {
                if (dist[u] == Long.MAX_VALUE) continue;
                for (Edge e : graph[u]) {
                    if (dist[u] + e.cost < dist[e.to]) {
                        dist[e.to] = dist[u] + e.cost;
                        hasPosCycle[e.to] = true;
                    }
                    if (hasPosCycle[u]) {
                        hasPosCycle[e.to] = true;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        if (hasPosCycle[N]) {
            System.out.println(-1);
        } else if (dist[N] == Long.MAX_VALUE) {
            System.out.println(0);
        } else {
            System.out.println(Math.max(0, -dist[N]));
        }
    }
}
test/1/claude_p02949_3P.java: 1-70 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static class Edge {
        int to, cost;
        Edge(int to, int cost) {
            this.to = to;
            this.cost = cost;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();
        int P = sc.nextInt();

        List<Edge>[] graph = new List[N + 1];
        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            graph[i] = new ArrayList<>();
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            int c = sc.nextInt();
            graph[a].add(new Edge(b, P - c));
        }

        long[] dist = new long[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(dist, Long.MAX_VALUE);
        dist[1] = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < N - 1; i++) {
            for (int v = 1; v <= N; v++) {
                if (dist[v] == Long.MAX_VALUE) continue;
                for (Edge e : graph[v]) {
                    if (dist[v] + e.cost < dist[e.to]) {
                        dist[e.to] = dist[v] + e.cost;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        boolean[] inNegCycle = new boolean[N + 1];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            for (int v = 1; v <= N; v++) {
                if (dist[v] == Long.MAX_VALUE) continue;
                for (Edge e : graph[v]) {
                    if (dist[v] + e.cost < dist[e.to]) {
                        dist[e.to] = dist[v] + e.cost;
                        inNegCycle[e.to] = true;
                    }
                    if (inNegCycle[v]) {
                        inNegCycle[e.to] = true;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        if (inNegCycle[N]) {
            System.out.println(-1);
        } else if (dist[N] == Long.MAX_VALUE) {
            System.out.println(0);
        } else {
            System.out.println(Math.max(0, -dist[N]));
        }
    }
}

train/1/claude_p02952_2P.java: 1-32 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        String nStr = String.valueOf(N);
        int digits = nStr.length();

        int count = 0;

        for (int d = 1; d < digits; d += 2) {
            if (d == 1) {
                count += 9;
            } else {
                count += 9 * (int)Math.pow(10, d - 1);
            }
        }

        if (digits % 2 == 1) {
            if (digits == 1) {
                count += N;
            } else {
                count += N - (int)Math.pow(10, digits - 1) + 1;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int max1 = Math.max(a[0], a[1]);
        int max2 = Math.min(a[0], a[1]);

        for (int i = 2; i < n; i++) {
            if (a[i] > max1) {
                max2 = max1;
                max1 = a[i];
            } else if (a[i] > max2) {
                max2 = a[i];
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (a[i] == max1) {
                System.out.println(max2);
            } else {
                System.out.println(max1);
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        int[][] jobs = new int[n][2];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            jobs[i][0] = sc.nextInt();
            jobs[i][1] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        Arrays.sort(jobs, (a, b) -> Integer.compare(a[1], b[1]));

        long currentTime = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            currentTime += jobs[i][0];
            if (currentTime > jobs[i][1]) {
                System.out.println("No");
                return;
            }
        }

        System.out.println("Yes");
    }
}

public class Main {

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {

train/1/claude_p02997_0P.java: 1-37 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        int maxK = (N - 1) * (N - 2) / 2;

        if (K > maxK) {
            System.out.println(-1);
            return;
        }

        List<int[]> edges = new ArrayList<>();

        for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
            edges.add(new int[]{1, i});
        }

        int currentK = maxK;

        for (int i = 2; i <= N && currentK > K; i++) {
            for (int j = i + 1; j <= N && currentK > K; j++) {
                edges.add(new int[]{i, j});
                currentK--;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(edges.size());
        for (int[] edge : edges) {
            System.out.println(edge[0] + " " + edge[1]);
        }
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03017_1P.java: 1-55 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int A = sc.nextInt() - 1;
        int B = sc.nextInt() - 1;
        int C = sc.nextInt() - 1;
        int D = sc.nextInt() - 1;
        String S = sc.next();

        Queue<int[]> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        Set<String> visited = new HashSet<>();

        queue.offer(new int[]{A, B});
        visited.add(A + "," + B);

        while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
            int[] curr = queue.poll();
            int snuke = curr[0];
            int fnuke = curr[1];

            if (snuke == C && fnuke == D) {
                System.out.println("Yes");
                return;
            }

            for (int jump = 1; jump <= 2; jump++) {
                int newSnuke = snuke + jump;
                if (newSnuke < N && S.charAt(newSnuke) == '.' && newSnuke != fnuke) {
                    String state = newSnuke + "," + fnuke;
                    if (!visited.contains(state)) {
                        visited.add(state);
                        queue.offer(new int[]{newSnuke, fnuke});
                    }
                }
            }

            for (int jump = 1; jump <= 2; jump++) {
                int newFnuke = fnuke + jump;
                if (newFnuke < N && S.charAt(newFnuke) == '.' && newFnuke != snuke) {
                    String state = snuke + "," + newFnuke;
                    if (!visited.contains(state)) {
                        visited.add(state);
                        queue.offer(new int[]{snuke, newFnuke});
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println("No");
    }
}

public class Main {

        Set<String> visited = new HashSet<>();

        queue.offer(new int[]{A, B});
        visited.add(A + "," + B);

        while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
            int[] curr = queue.poll();
            int snuke = curr[0];
            int fnuke = curr[1];

            if (snuke == C && fnuke == D) {
                System.out.println("Yes");
                return;
            }

                int newSnuke = snuke + jump;

                    String state = newSnuke + "," + fnuke;

                        visited.add(state);
                        queue.offer(new int[]{newSnuke, fnuke});

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        List<Restaurant> restaurants = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            String city = sc.next();
            int score = sc.nextInt();
            restaurants.add(new Restaurant(i + 1, city, score));
        }

        restaurants.sort((a, b) -> {
            int cityComparison = a.city.compareTo(b.city);
            if (cityComparison != 0) {
                return cityComparison;
            }
            return Integer.compare(b.score, a.score);
        });

        for (Restaurant restaurant : restaurants) {
            System.out.println(restaurant.id);
        }
    }

    static class Restaurant {
        int id;
        String city;
        int score;

        Restaurant(int id, String city, int score) {
            this.id = id;
            this.city = city;
            this.score = score;
        }
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03031_0P.java: 1-51 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        int[][] bulbSwitches = new int[M][];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            bulbSwitches[i] = new int[k];
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                bulbSwitches[i][j] = sc.nextInt() - 1;
            }
        }

        int[] p = new int[M];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            p[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int count = 0;

        for (int mask = 0; mask < (1 << N); mask++) {
            boolean allLit = true;

            for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
                int onCount = 0;

                for (int switchIdx : bulbSwitches[i]) {
                    if ((mask & (1 << switchIdx)) != 0) {
                        onCount++;
                    }
                }

                if (onCount % 2 != p[i]) {
                    allLit = false;
                    break;
                }
            }

            if (allLit) {
                count++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03043_0P.java: 1-33 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        double totalProbability = 0.0;

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            double winProbability = 0.0;

            if (i >= K) {
                winProbability = 1.0;
            } else {
                int headsNeeded = 0;
                int current = i;
                while (current < K) {
                    current *= 2;
                    headsNeeded++;
                }

                winProbability = Math.pow(0.5, headsNeeded);
            }

            totalProbability += winProbability / N;
        }

        System.out.println(totalProbability);
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03048_0P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int R = sc.nextInt();
        int G = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        int count = 0;

        for (int r = 0; r * R <= N; r++) {
            for (int g = 0; r * R + g * G <= N; g++) {
                int remaining = N - r * R - g * G;
                if (remaining >= 0 && remaining % B == 0) {
                    count++;
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

        int count = 0;

        for (int r = 0; r * R <= N; r++) {
            for (int g = 0; r * R + g * G <= N; g++) {
                int remaining = N - r * R - g * G;
                if (remaining >= 0 && remaining % B == 0) {
                    count++;
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
    }

train/1/claude_p03060_2P.java: 1-40 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] v = new int[n];
        int[] c = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            v[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            c[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int maxProfit = 0;

        for (int mask = 0; mask < (1 << n); mask++) {
            int totalValue = 0;
            int totalCost = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                if ((mask & (1 << i)) != 0) {
                    totalValue += v[i];
                    totalCost += c[i];
                }
            }

            int profit = totalValue - totalCost;
            maxProfit = Math.max(maxProfit, profit);
        }

        System.out.println(maxProfit);
        sc.close();
    }
}
test/1/claude_p03060_4P.java: 1-40 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] values = new int[n];
        int[] costs = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            values[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            costs[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int maxProfit = 0;

        for (int mask = 0; mask < (1 << n); mask++) {
            int totalValue = 0;
            int totalCost = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                if ((mask & (1 << i)) != 0) {
                    totalValue += values[i];
                    totalCost += costs[i];
                }
            }

            int profit = totalValue - totalCost;
            maxProfit = Math.max(maxProfit, profit);
        }

        System.out.println(maxProfit);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03063_0P.java: 1-32 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        String s = sc.next();

        int minChanges = n;

        for (int cut = 0; cut <= n; cut++) {
            int changes = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < cut; i++) {
                if (s.charAt(i) == '#') {
                    changes++;
                }
            }

            for (int i = cut; i < n; i++) {
                if (s.charAt(i) == '.') {
                    changes++;
                }
            }

            minChanges = Math.min(minChanges, changes);
        }

        System.out.println(minChanges);
    }
}

        int b = sc.nextInt();
        int c = sc.nextInt();
        int d = sc.nextInt();
        int e = sc.nextInt();

                if (distance > k) {

                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println("Yay!");
    }

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        long N = sc.nextLong();
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();
        long C = sc.nextLong();
        long D = sc.nextLong();
        long E = sc.nextLong();

        long minCapacity = Math.min(A, Math.min(B, Math.min(C, Math.min(D, E))));

        long timeForBottleneck = (N + minCapacity - 1) / minCapacity;
        long totalTime = timeForBottleneck + 4;

        System.out.println(totalTime);
        sc.close();
    }
}

Class 532:   2 fragments, nominal size 64 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p03078_3P.java: 1-75 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int X = sc.nextInt();
        int Y = sc.nextInt();
        int Z = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        long[] A = new long[X];
        long[] B = new long[Y];
        long[] C = new long[Z];

        for (int i = 0; i < X; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < Y; i++) {
            B[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < Z; i++) {
            C[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        Arrays.sort(A);
        Arrays.sort(B);
        Arrays.sort(C);
        for (int i = 0; i < X / 2; i++) {
            long temp = A[i];
            A[i] = A[X - 1 - i];
            A[X - 1 - i] = temp;
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < Y / 2; i++) {
            long temp = B[i];
            B[i] = B[Y - 1 - i];
            B[Y - 1 - i] = temp;
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < Z / 2; i++) {
            long temp = C[i];
            C[i] = C[Z - 1 - i];
            C[Z - 1 - i] = temp;
        }

        PriorityQueue<long[]> pq = new PriorityQueue<>((a, b) -> Long.compare(b[0], a[0]));
        Set<String> visited = new HashSet<>();

        pq.offer(new long[]{A[0] + B[0] + C[0], 0, 0, 0});
        visited.add("0,0,0");

        for (int count = 0; count < K; count++) {
            long[] current = pq.poll();
            long sum = current[0];
            int i = (int)current[1];
            int j = (int)current[2];
            int k = (int)current[3];

            System.out.println(sum);

            if (i + 1 < X && !visited.contains((i + 1) + "," + j + "," + k)) {
                pq.offer(new long[]{A[i + 1] + B[j] + C[k], i + 1, j, k});
                visited.add((i + 1) + "," + j + "," + k);
            }
            if (j + 1 < Y && !visited.contains(i + "," + (j + 1) + "," + k)) {
                pq.offer(new long[]{A[i] + B[j + 1] + C[k], i, j + 1, k});
                visited.add(i + "," + (j + 1) + "," + k);
            }
            if (k + 1 < Z && !visited.contains(i + "," + j + "," + (k + 1))) {
                pq.offer(new long[]{A[i] + B[j] + C[k + 1], i, j, k + 1});
                visited.add(i + "," + j + "," + (k + 1));
            }
        }
    }
}

                pq.offer(new long[]{A[i + 1] + B[j] + C[k], i + 1, j, k});
                visited.add((i + 1) + "," + j + "," + k);
            }
            if (j + 1 < Y && !visited.contains(i + "," + (j + 1) + "," + k)) {
                pq.offer(new long[]{A[i] + B[j + 1] + C[k], i, j + 1, k});
                visited.add(i + "," + (j + 1) + "," + k);
            }
            if (k + 1 < Z && !visited.contains(i + "," + j + "," + (k + 1))) {
                pq.offer(new long[]{A[i] + B[j] + C[k + 1], i, j, k + 1});
                visited.add(i + "," + j + "," + (k + 1));
            }
        }
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03082_4P.java: 1-48 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static final int MOD = 1000000007;
    static int N, X;
    static int[] S;
    static Map<String, Long> memo = new HashMap<>();

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        N = sc.nextInt();
        X = sc.nextInt();
        S = new int[N];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            S[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int fullMask = (1 << N) - 1;
        long result = solve(X, fullMask);
        System.out.println(result);
    }

    static long solve(int currentValue, int mask) {
        if (mask == 0) {
            return currentValue;
        }

        String key = currentValue + "," + mask;
        if (memo.containsKey(key)) {
            return memo.get(key);
        }

        long sum = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if ((mask & (1 << i)) != 0) {
                int newValue = currentValue % S[i];
                int newMask = mask ^ (1 << i);
                sum = (sum + solve(newValue, newMask)) % MOD;
            }
        }

        memo.put(key, sum);
        return sum;
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    static final int MOD = 1000000007;
    static int N, X;
    static int[] S;
    static Map<String, Long> memo = new HashMap<>();

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        N = sc.nextInt();
        X = sc.nextInt();
        S = new int[N];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            S[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int allMask = (1 << N) - 1;
        long result = solve(X, allMask);
        System.out.println(result);
    }

    static long solve(int currentValue, int mask) {
        if (mask == 0) {
            return currentValue;
        }

        String key = currentValue + "," + mask;
        if (memo.containsKey(key)) {
            return memo.get(key);
        }

        long sum = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if ((mask & (1 << i)) != 0) {
                int newValue = currentValue % S[i];
                int newMask = mask ^ (1 << i);
                sum = (sum + solve(newValue, newMask)) % MOD;
            }
        }

        memo.put(key, sum);
        return sum;
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03106_3P.java: 1-33 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        int gcd = gcd(A, B);

        List<Integer> divisors = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 1; i <= gcd; i++) {
            if (gcd % i == 0) {
                divisors.add(i);
            }
        }

        Collections.sort(divisors, Collections.reverseOrder());

        System.out.println(divisors.get(K - 1));
    }

    private static int gcd(int a, int b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            int temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        double total = 0.0;
        double btcRate = 380000.0;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            double amount = sc.nextDouble();
            String currency = sc.next();

            if (currency.equals("JPY")) {
                total += amount;
            } else if (currency.equals("BTC")) {
                total += amount * btcRate;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(total);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03126_4P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        int[] foodCount = new int[M + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int K = sc.nextInt();
            for (int j = 0; j < K; j++) {
                int food = sc.nextInt();
                foodCount[food]++;
            }
        }

        int result = 0;
        for (int i = 1; i <= M; i++) {
            if (foodCount[i] == N) {
                result++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(result);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03136_1P.java: 1-33 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] sides = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            sides[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int maxSide = 0;
        int totalSum = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            maxSide = Math.max(maxSide, sides[i]);
            totalSum += sides[i];
        }

        int sumOfOthers = totalSum - maxSide;

        if (maxSide < sumOfOthers) {
            System.out.println("Yes");
        } else {
            System.out.println("No");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}
test/1/claude_p03136_0P.java: 1-33 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] sides = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            sides[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int maxSide = 0;
        int totalSum = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            maxSide = Math.max(maxSide, sides[i]);
            totalSum += sides[i];
        }

        int sumOfOthers = totalSum - maxSide;

        if (maxSide < sumOfOthers) {
            System.out.println("Yes");
        } else {
            System.out.println("No");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}
train/1/claude_p03136_3P.java: 1-33 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] sides = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            sides[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int maxSide = 0;
        int totalSum = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            maxSide = Math.max(maxSide, sides[i]);
            totalSum += sides[i];
        }

        int sumOfOthers = totalSum - maxSide;

        if (maxSide < sumOfOthers) {
            System.out.println("Yes");
        } else {
            System.out.println("No");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03162_2P.java: 1-33 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        int[][] activities = new int[n][3];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            activities[i][0] = sc.nextInt();
            activities[i][1] = sc.nextInt();
            activities[i][2] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int[][] dp = new int[n][3];

        dp[0][0] = activities[0][0];
        dp[0][1] = activities[0][1];
        dp[0][2] = activities[0][2];

        for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) {
            dp[i][0] = activities[i][0] + Math.max(dp[i-1][1], dp[i-1][2]);
            dp[i][1] = activities[i][1] + Math.max(dp[i-1][0], dp[i-1][2]);
            dp[i][2] = activities[i][2] + Math.max(dp[i-1][0], dp[i-1][1]);
        }

        int result = Math.max(Math.max(dp[n-1][0], dp[n-1][1]), dp[n-1][2]);
        System.out.println(result);

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03164_3P.java: 1-49 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long W = sc.nextLong();

        int[] w = new int[N];
        int[] v = new int[N];
        int totalValue = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            w[i] = sc.nextInt();
            v[i] = sc.nextInt();
            totalValue += v[i];
        }

        long[][] dp = new long[N + 1][totalValue + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i <= N; i++) {
            Arrays.fill(dp[i], Long.MAX_VALUE);
        }

        for (int i = 0; i <= N; i++) {
            dp[i][0] = 0;
        }

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j <= totalValue; j++) {
                dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j];

                if (j >= v[i-1] && dp[i-1][j - v[i-1]] != Long.MAX_VALUE) {
                    dp[i][j] = Math.min(dp[i][j], dp[i-1][j - v[i-1]] + w[i-1]);
                }
            }
        }

        int maxValue = 0;
        for (int j = 0; j <= totalValue; j++) {
            if (dp[N][j] <= W) {
                maxValue = j;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(maxValue);
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03165_2P.java: 1-42 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.nextLine();
        String t = sc.nextLine();

        int m = s.length();
        int n = t.length();

        int[][] dp = new int[m + 1][n + 1];

        for (int i = 1; i <= m; i++) {
            for (int j = 1; j <= n; j++) {
                if (s.charAt(i - 1) == t.charAt(j - 1)) {
                    dp[i][j] = dp[i - 1][j - 1] + 1;
                } else {
                    dp[i][j] = Math.max(dp[i - 1][j], dp[i][j - 1]);
                }
            }
        }

        StringBuilder lcs = new StringBuilder();
        int i = m, j = n;

        while (i > 0 && j > 0) {
            if (s.charAt(i - 1) == t.charAt(j - 1)) {
                lcs.append(s.charAt(i - 1));
                i--;
                j--;
            } else if (dp[i - 1][j] > dp[i][j - 1]) {
                i--;
            } else {
                j--;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(lcs.reverse().toString());
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long[] a = new long[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long[][] dp = new long[n][n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            dp[i][i] = a[i];
        }

        for (int len = 2; len <= n; len++) {
            for (int i = 0; i <= n - len; i++) {
                int j = i + len - 1;
                long takeLeft = a[i] - dp[i + 1][j];
                long takeRight = a[j] - dp[i][j - 1];
                dp[i][j] = Math.max(takeLeft, takeRight);
            }
        }

        System.out.println(dp[0][n - 1]);
        sc.close();
    }
}
test/1/claude_p03171_3P.java: 1-32 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long[] a = new long[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long[][] dp = new long[n][n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            dp[i][i] = a[i];
        }

        for (int len = 2; len <= n; len++) {
            for (int i = 0; i <= n - len; i++) {
                int j = i + len - 1;
                long takeLeft = a[i] - dp[i + 1][j];
                long takeRight = a[j] - dp[i][j - 1];
                dp[i][j] = Math.max(takeLeft, takeRight);
            }
        }

        System.out.println(dp[0][n - 1]);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03194_0P.java: 1-34 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long N = sc.nextLong();
        long P = sc.nextLong();

        long result = 1;

        for (long i = 2; i * i <= P; i++) {
            long count = 0;
            while (P % i == 0) {
                P /= i;
                count++;
            }
            if (count > 0) {
                long gcdPower = count / N;
                for (long j = 0; j < gcdPower; j++) {
                    result *= i;
                }
            }
        }

        if (P > 1) {
            if (N == 1) {
                result *= P;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(result);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();

        int operations = 0;
        int wCount = 0;

        for (int i = s.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'W') {
                wCount++;
            } else {
                operations += wCount;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(operations);
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03207_0P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] prices = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            prices[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int maxPrice = prices[0];
        for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) {
            if (prices[i] > maxPrice) {
                maxPrice = prices[i];
            }
        }

        int total = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            total += prices[i];
        }
        total -= maxPrice / 2;

        System.out.println(total);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03239_1P.java: 1-32 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int T = sc.nextInt();

        int minCost = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        boolean found = false;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int cost = sc.nextInt();
            int time = sc.nextInt();

            if (time <= T) {
                found = true;
                minCost = Math.min(minCost, cost);
            }
        }

        if (found) {
            System.out.println(minCost);
        } else {
            System.out.println("TLE");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

        int minCost = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        boolean foundRoute = false;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int cost = sc.nextInt();
            int time = sc.nextInt();

            if (time <= T) {
                foundRoute = true;
                minCost = Math.min(minCost, cost);
            }
        }

        if (foundRoute) {
            System.out.println(minCost);
        } else {
            System.out.println("TLE");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

Class 559:   2 fragments, nominal size 22 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p03274_4P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        int[] x = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            x[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int minTime = Integer.MAX_VALUE;

        for (int i = 0; i <= N - K; i++) {
            int left = x[i];
            int right = x[i + K - 1];

            int time1 = Math.abs(left) + Math.abs(right - left);

            int time2 = Math.abs(right) + Math.abs(right - left);

            minTime = Math.min(minTime, Math.min(time1, time2));
        }

        System.out.println(minTime);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03283_4P.java: 1-33 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();
        int Q = sc.nextInt();

        int[][] count = new int[N + 1][N + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int L = sc.nextInt();
            int R = sc.nextInt();

            for (int p = 1; p <= L; p++) {
                for (int q = R; q <= N; q++) {
                    count[p][q]++;
                }
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < Q; i++) {
            int p = sc.nextInt();
            int q = sc.nextInt();
            System.out.println(count[p][q]);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

Class 563:   4 fragments, nominal size 24 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/claude_p03296_1P.java: 1-32 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int spells = 0;
        int i = 0;

        while (i < n) {
            int j = i;
            while (j < n && a[j] == a[i]) {
                j++;
            }

            int groupSize = j - i;
            spells += groupSize / 2;

            i = j;
        }

        System.out.println(spells);
        sc.close();
    }
}

        int w = sc.nextInt();

train/1/claude_p03308_2P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int max = a[0];
        int min = a[0];

        for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) {
            if (a[i] > max) {
                max = a[i];
            }
            if (a[i] < min) {
                min = a[i];
            }
        }

        System.out.println(max - min);

        sc.close();
    }
}

        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        int min = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        int max = Integer.MIN_VALUE;

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            min = Math.min(min, a);
            max = Math.max(max, a);
        }

        System.out.println(max - min);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/claude_p03309_4P.java: 1-26 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int[] b = new int[n];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            b[i] = a - (i + 1);
        }

        Arrays.sort(b);

        int median = b[(n - 1) / 2];

        long sadness = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            sadness += Math.abs(b[i] - median);
        }

        System.out.println(sadness);
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        long[] a = new long[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long[] prefix = new long[n + 1];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            prefix[i + 1] = prefix[i] + a[i];
        }

        long minDiff = Long.MAX_VALUE;

        for (int i = 1; i < n - 2; i++) {
            for (int j = i + 1; j < n - 1; j++) {
                for (int k = j + 1; k < n; k++) {
                    long p = prefix[i] - prefix[0];
                    long q = prefix[j] - prefix[i];
                    long r = prefix[k] - prefix[j];
                    long s = prefix[n] - prefix[k];

                    long max = Math.max(Math.max(p, q), Math.max(r, s));
                    long min = Math.min(Math.min(p, q), Math.min(r, s));

                    minDiff = Math.min(minDiff, max - min);
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(minDiff);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = scanner.nextLine();

        int result = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            char c = s.charAt(i);
            if (c == '+') {
                result++;
            } else if (c == '-') {
                result--;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(result);
        scanner.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        int sum = 0;
        int temp = N;
        while (temp > 0) {
            sum += temp % 10;
            temp /= 10;
        }

        if (N % sum == 0) {
            System.out.println("Yes");
        } else {
            System.out.println("No");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}
