Class 894:   3 fragments, nominal size 41 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/gemini_p03031_0P.java: 1-47 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        int[][] s = new int[M][];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            s[i] = new int[k];
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                s[i][j] = sc.nextInt() - 1;
            }
        }

        int[] p = new int[M];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            p[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int count = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < (1 << N); i++) {
            boolean allBulbsLighted = true;
            for (int j = 0; j < M; j++) {
                int onSwitchCount = 0;
                for (int switchIdx : s[j]) {
                    if (((i >> switchIdx) & 1) == 1) {
                        onSwitchCount++;
                    }
                }
                if (onSwitchCount % 2 != p[j]) {
                    allBulbsLighted = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (allBulbsLighted) {
                count++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
        sc.close();
    }
}

        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {

        }

        int count = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < (1 << N); i++) {
            boolean allBulbsLighted = true;
            for (int j = 0; j < M; j++) {
                int onCount = 0;
                for (int switchIdx : s[j]) {
                    if (((i >> switchIdx) & 1) == 1) {
                        onCount++;
                    }
                }
                if (onCount % 2 != p[j]) {
                    allBulbsLighted = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (allBulbsLighted) {
                count++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);

        sc.close();
    }
}
train/1/gemini_p03031_3P.java: 1-47 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        int[][] s = new int[M][];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            int k = sc.nextInt();
            s[i] = new int[k];
            for (int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
                s[i][j] = sc.nextInt() - 1;
            }
        }

        int[] p = new int[M];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            p[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int count = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < (1 << N); i++) {
            boolean allBulbsLighted = true;
            for (int j = 0; j < M; j++) {
                int onSwitchCount = 0;
                for (int switchIdx : s[j]) {
                    if (((i >> switchIdx) & 1) == 1) {
                        onSwitchCount++;
                    }
                }
                if (onSwitchCount % 2 != p[j]) {
                    allBulbsLighted = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (allBulbsLighted) {
                count++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(count);
        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        sc.close();

        int firstTwo = Integer.parseInt(s.substring(0, 2));
        int lastTwo = Integer.parseInt(s.substring(2, 4));

        boolean isYYMM = isValidMonth(lastTwo);
        boolean isMMYY = isValidMonth(firstTwo);

        if (isYYMM && isMMYY) {
            System.out.println("AMBIGUOUS");
        } else if (isYYMM) {
            System.out.println("YYMM");
        } else if (isMMYY) {
            System.out.println("MMYY");
        } else {
            System.out.println("NA");
        }
    }

    private static boolean isValidMonth(int month) {
        return month >= 1 && month <= 12;
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int R = sc.nextInt();
        int G = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        sc.close();

        long count = 0;
        for (int r = 0; r * R <= N; r++) {
            for (int g = 0; r * R + g * G <= N; g++) {
                int remaining = N - (r * R + g * G);
                if (remaining % B == 0) {
                    count++;
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] V = new int[N];
        int[] C = new int[N];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            V[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            C[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int maxProfit = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if (V[i] - C[i] > 0) {
                maxProfit += (V[i] - C[i]);
            }
        }
        System.out.println(maxProfit);
        sc.close();
    }
}

Class 899:   2 fragments, nominal size 26 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/gemini_p03104_2P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {

    private static long xorSumUpToN(long n) {
        long remainder = n % 4;
        if (remainder == 0) {
            return n;
        } else if (remainder == 1) {
            return 1;
        } else if (remainder == 2) {
            return n + 1;
        } else {
            return 0;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();
        sc.close();

        long result = xorSumUpToN(B) ^ xorSumUpToN(A - 1);
        System.out.println(result);
    }
}
test/1/gemini_p03104_0P.java: 1-29 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {

    private static long xorSumUpTo(long N) {
        long remainder = N % 4;
        if (remainder == 0) {
            return N;
        } else if (remainder == 1) {
            return 1;
        } else if (remainder == 2) {
            return N + 1;
        } else {
            return 0;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();
        sc.close();

        long result = xorSumUpTo(B) ^ xorSumUpTo(A - 1);

        System.out.println(result);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        int redCount = 0;
        int blueCount = 0;

        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            if (c == '0') {
                redCount++;
            } else {
                blueCount++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(Math.min(redCount, blueCount) * 2);

        sc.close();
    }

train/1/gemini_p03126_0P.java: 1-30 
import java.util.HashSet;
import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.Set;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();

        Set<Integer> commonFoods = new HashSet<>();
        for (int i = 1; i <= M; i++) {
            commonFoods.add(i);
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int K = sc.nextInt();
            Set<Integer> currentPersonFoods = new HashSet<>();
            for (int j = 0; j < K; j++) {
                currentPersonFoods.add(sc.nextInt());
            }
            commonFoods.retainAll(currentPersonFoods);
        }

        System.out.println(commonFoods.size());

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03162_3P.java: 1-29 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        int[][] dp = new int[N][3];

        dp[0][0] = sc.nextInt();
        dp[0][1] = sc.nextInt();
        dp[0][2] = sc.nextInt();

        for (int i = 1; i < N; i++) {
            int a = sc.nextInt();
            int b = sc.nextInt();
            int c = sc.nextInt();

            dp[i][0] = a + Math.max(dp[i - 1][1], dp[i - 1][2]);
            dp[i][1] = b + Math.max(dp[i - 1][0], dp[i - 1][2]);
            dp[i][2] = c + Math.max(dp[i - 1][0], dp[i - 1][1]);
        }

        System.out.println(Math.max(dp[N - 1][0], Math.max(dp[N - 1][1], dp[N - 1][2])));

        sc.close();
    }
}

        int[][] dp = new int[N][3];

        dp[0][0] = sc.nextInt();
        dp[0][1] = sc.nextInt();
        dp[0][2] = sc.nextInt();

        for (int i = 1; i < N; i++) {
            int a_i = sc.nextInt();
            int b_i = sc.nextInt();
            int c_i = sc.nextInt();

            dp[i][0] = a_i + Math.max(dp[i - 1][1], dp[i - 1][2]);
            dp[i][1] = b_i + Math.max(dp[i - 1][0], dp[i - 1][2]);
            dp[i][2] = c_i + Math.max(dp[i - 1][0], dp[i - 1][1]);
        }

        System.out.println(Math.max(dp[N - 1][0], Math.max(dp[N - 1][1], dp[N - 1][2])));

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03163_4P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();

        long[] dp = new long[W + 1];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            int w = sc.nextInt();
            int v = sc.nextInt();
            for (int j = W; j >= w; j--) {
                dp[j] = Math.max(dp[j], dp[j - w] + v);
            }
        }

        long maxValue = 0;
        for (long val : dp) {
            maxValue = Math.max(maxValue, val);
        }

        System.out.println(maxValue);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03309_2P.java: 1-32 
import java.util.Arrays;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long[] B = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            long A_i = sc.nextLong();
            B[i] = A_i - (i + 1);
        }

        Arrays.sort(B);

        long median;
        if (N % 2 == 1) {
            median = B[N / 2];
        } else {
            median = B[N / 2 - 1];
        }

        long sadness = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            sadness += Math.abs(B[i] - median);
        }

        System.out.println(sadness);
        sc.close();
    }
}

Class 910:   3 fragments, nominal size 25 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/gemini_p03331_4P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static int sumDigits(int n) {
        int sum = 0;
        String s = String.valueOf(n);
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            sum += Character.getNumericValue(c);
        }
        return sum;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        sc.close();

        int minSumOfDigits = Integer.MAX_VALUE;

        for (int A = 1; A < N; A++) {
            int B = N - A;
            int currentSum = sumDigits(A) + sumDigits(B);
            if (currentSum < minSumOfDigits) {
                minSumOfDigits = currentSum;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(minSumOfDigits);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int a = sc.nextInt();
        int b = sc.nextInt();
        int c = sc.nextInt();
        int d = sc.nextInt();

        boolean directCommunicateAC = Math.abs(a - c) <= d;

        boolean indirectCommunicateABC = Math.abs(a - b) <= d && Math.abs(b - c) <= d;

        if (directCommunicateAC || indirectCommunicateABC) {
            System.out.println("Yes");
        } else {
            System.out.println("No");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int a = sc.nextInt();
        int b = sc.nextInt();
        sc.close();

        int count = 0;
        int[] daysInMonth = {0, 31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};

        for (int month = 1; month <= a; month++) {
            if (month <= daysInMonth[month]) {
                if (month < a) {
                    count++;
                } else if (month == a) {
                    if (month <= b) {
                        count++;
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(count);
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03364_2P.java: 1-42 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        char[][] S = new char[N][N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            String row = sc.next();
            for (int j = 0; j < N; j++) {
                S[i][j] = row.charAt(j);
            }
        }

        int goodBoardCount = 0;

        for (int A = 0; A < N; A++) {
            for (int B = 0; B < N; B++) {
                boolean isGoodBoard = true;
                for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
                    for (int j = 0; j < N; j++) {
                        if (S[(i + A) % N][(j + B) % N] != S[(j + A) % N][(i + B) % N]) {
                            isGoodBoard = false;
                            break;
                        }
                    }
                    if (!isGoodBoard) {
                        break;
                    }
                }
                if (isGoodBoard) {
                    goodBoardCount++;
                }
            }
        }

        System.out.println(goodBoardCount);
        sc.close();
    }
}

        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int M = sc.nextInt();
        int X = sc.nextInt();

        int[] A = new int[M];
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        int costTo0 = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            if (A[i] < X) {
                costTo0++;
            }
        }

        int costToN = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < M; i++) {
            if (A[i] > X) {
                costToN++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(Math.min(costTo0, costToN));

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03379_2P.java: 1-32 
import java.util.Arrays;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] X = new int[N];
        int[] sortedX = new int[N];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            X[i] = sc.nextInt();
            sortedX[i] = X[i];
        }

        Arrays.sort(sortedX);

        int median1 = sortedX[N / 2 - 1];
        int median2 = sortedX[N / 2];

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if (X[i] <= median1) {
                System.out.println(median2);
            } else {
                System.out.println(median1);
            }
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Arrays;
import java.util.Collections;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        Integer[] a = new Integer[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }

        Arrays.sort(a, Collections.reverseOrder());

        int aliceScore = 0;
        int bobScore = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if (i % 2 == 0) {
                aliceScore += a[i];
            } else {
                bobScore += a[i];
            }
        }

        System.out.println(aliceScore - bobScore);

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03449_1P.java: 1-31 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[][] A = new int[2][N];
        for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < N; j++) {
                A[i][j] = sc.nextInt();
            }
        }
        sc.close();

        int maxCandies = 0;

        for (int k = 0; k < N; k++) {
            int currentCandies = 0;
            for (int j = 0; j <= k; j++) {
                currentCandies += A[0][j];
            }
            for (int j = k; j < N; j++) {
                currentCandies += A[1][j];
            }
            maxCandies = Math.max(maxCandies, currentCandies);
        }

        System.out.println(maxCandies);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        long X = sc.nextLong();
        long Y = sc.nextLong();
        sc.close();

        int length = 0;
        long current = X;
        while (current <= Y) {
            length++;
            if (Y / 2 < current) {
                break;
            }
            current *= 2;
        }

        System.out.println(length);
    }
}

Class 924:   2 fragments, nominal size 43 lines, similarity 100%

train/1/gemini_p03576_2P.java: 1-51 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        long[] x = new long[N];
        long[] y = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            x[i] = sc.nextLong();
            y[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long minArea = Long.MAX_VALUE;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < N; j++) {
                long x1 = x[i];
                long x2 = x[j];

                for (int a = 0; a < N; a++) {
                    for (int b = 0; b < N; b++) {
                        long y1 = y[a];
                        long y2 = y[b];

                        long left = Math.min(x1, x2);
                        long right = Math.max(x1, x2);
                        long bottom = Math.min(y1, y2);
                        long top = Math.max(y1, y2);

                        int count = 0;
                        for (int p = 0; p < N; p++) {
                            if (x[p] >= left && x[p] <= right && y[p] >= bottom && y[p] <= top) {
                                count++;
                            }
                        }

                        if (count >= K) {
                            long area = (right - left) * (top - bottom);
                            minArea = Math.min(minArea, area);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(minArea);
        sc.close();
    }
}
test/1/gemini_p03576_4P.java: 1-51 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        long[] x = new long[N];
        long[] y = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            x[i] = sc.nextLong();
            y[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long minArea = Long.MAX_VALUE;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < N; j++) {
                long x1 = x[i];
                long x2 = x[j];

                for (int m = 0; m < N; m++) {
                    for (int n = 0; n < N; n++) {
                        long y1 = y[m];
                        long y2 = y[n];

                        long minX = Math.min(x1, x2);
                        long maxX = Math.max(x1, x2);
                        long minY = Math.min(y1, y2);
                        long maxY = Math.max(y1, y2);

                        int count = 0;
                        for (int p = 0; p < N; p++) {
                            if (x[p] >= minX && x[p] <= maxX && y[p] >= minY && y[p] <= maxY) {
                                count++;
                            }
                        }

                        if (count >= K) {
                            long area = (maxX - minX) * (maxY - minY);
                            minArea = Math.min(minArea, area);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(minArea);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03612_1P.java: 1-25 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] p = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            p[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        sc.close();

        int operations = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            if (p[i] == i + 1) {
                operations++;
                if (i + 1 < N) {
                    i++;
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(operations);
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03633_1P.java: 1-35 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {

    private static long gcd(long a, long b) {
        while (b != 0) {
            long temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;
    }

    private static long lcm(long a, long b) {
        if (a == 0 || b == 0) return 0;
        return (a / gcd(a, b)) * b;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = scanner.nextInt();

        long resultLcm = 1;

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            long Ti = scanner.nextLong();
            resultLcm = lcm(resultLcm, Ti);
        }

        System.out.println(resultLcm);

        scanner.close();
    }
}

public class Main {

            long temp = b;
            b = a % b;
            a = temp;
        }
        return a;

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        long resultLcm = 1;

train/1/gemini_p03640_4P.java: 1-49 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int H = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        sc.close();

        int[][] grid = new int[H][W];
        int colorIndex = 0;
        int count = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            if (i % 2 == 0) {
                for (int j = 0; j < W; j++) {
                    grid[i][j] = colorIndex + 1;
                    count++;
                    if (count == a[colorIndex]) {
                        colorIndex++;
                        count = 0;
                    }
                }
            } else {
                for (int j = W - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
                    grid[i][j] = colorIndex + 1;
                    count++;
                    if (count == a[colorIndex]) {
                        colorIndex++;
                        count = 0;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < W; j++) {
                System.out.print(grid[i][j] + (j == W - 1 ? "" : " "));
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int A = sc.nextInt();
        int B = sc.nextInt();

        if (A % 3 == 0) {
            System.out.println("Possible");
        }
        else if (B % 3 == 0) {
            System.out.println("Possible");
        }
        else if ((A + B) % 3 == 0) {
            System.out.println("Possible");
        }
        else {
            System.out.println("Impossible");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03660_0P.java: 1-69 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        List<List<Integer>> adj = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i <= N; i++) {
            adj.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < N - 1; i++) {
            int u = sc.nextInt();
            int v = sc.nextInt();
            adj.get(u).add(v);
            adj.get(v).add(u);
        }

        int[] distFennec = new int[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(distFennec, -1);
        Queue<Integer> qFennec = new LinkedList<>();
        qFennec.add(1);
        distFennec[1] = 0;
        while (!qFennec.isEmpty()) {
            int u = qFennec.poll();
            for (int v : adj.get(u)) {
                if (distFennec[v] == -1) {
                    distFennec[v] = distFennec[u] + 1;
                    qFennec.add(v);
                }
            }
        }

        int[] distSnuke = new int[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(distSnuke, -1);
        Queue<Integer> qSnuke = new LinkedList<>();
        qSnuke.add(N);
        distSnuke[N] = 0;
        while (!qSnuke.isEmpty()) {
            int u = qSnuke.poll();
            for (int v : adj.get(u)) {
                if (distSnuke[v] == -1) {
                    distSnuke[v] = distSnuke[u] + 1;
                    qSnuke.add(v);
                }
            }
        }

        int fennecCount = 0;
        int snukeCount = 0;

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            if (distFennec[i] <= distSnuke[i]) {
                fennecCount++;
            } else {
                snukeCount++;
            }
        }

        if (fennecCount > snukeCount) {
            System.out.println("Fennec");
        } else {
            System.out.println("Snuke");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        for (int i = 0; i <= N; i++) {
            adj.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < N - 1; i++) {
            int u = sc.nextInt();
            int v = sc.nextInt();
            adj.get(u).add(v);
            adj.get(v).add(u);
        }

        int[] distFennec = new int[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(distFennec, -1);
        Queue<Integer> qFennec = new LinkedList<>();
        qFennec.offer(1);
        distFennec[1] = 0;

        while (!qFennec.isEmpty()) {
            int u = qFennec.poll();
            for (int v : adj.get(u)) {
                if (distFennec[v] == -1) {
                    distFennec[v] = distFennec[u] + 1;
                    qFennec.offer(v);
                }

train/1/gemini_p03662_3P.java: 1-72 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();

        List<List<Integer>> adj = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i <= N; i++) {
            adj.add(new ArrayList<>());
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < N - 1; i++) {
            int u = sc.nextInt();
            int v = sc.nextInt();
            adj.get(u).add(v);
            adj.get(v).add(u);
        }

        int[] distFennec = new int[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(distFennec, -1);
        Queue<Integer> qFennec = new LinkedList<>();
        qFennec.add(1);
        distFennec[1] = 0;

        while (!qFennec.isEmpty()) {
            int u = qFennec.poll();
            for (int v : adj.get(u)) {
                if (distFennec[v] == -1) {
                    distFennec[v] = distFennec[u] + 1;
                    qFennec.add(v);
                }
            }
        }

        int[] distSnuke = new int[N + 1];
        Arrays.fill(distSnuke, -1);
        Queue<Integer> qSnuke = new LinkedList<>();
        qSnuke.add(N);
        distSnuke[N] = 0;

        while (!qSnuke.isEmpty()) {
            int u = qSnuke.poll();
            for (int v : adj.get(u)) {
                if (distSnuke[v] == -1) {
                    distSnuke[v] = distSnuke[u] + 1;
                    qSnuke.add(v);
                }
            }
        }

        int fennecCount = 0;
        int snukeCount = 0;

        for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) {
            if (distFennec[i] <= distSnuke[i]) {
                fennecCount++;
            } else {
                snukeCount++;
            }
        }

        if (fennecCount > snukeCount) {
            System.out.println("Fennec");
        } else {
            System.out.println("Snuke");
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03689_2P.java: 1-39 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int H = sc.nextInt();
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int h = sc.nextInt();
        int w = sc.nextInt();

        if (H % h == 0 && W % w == 0) {
            System.out.println("No");
            return;
        }

        System.out.println("Yes");
        long[][] matrix = new long[H][W];

        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < W; j++) {
                if ((i + 1) % h == 0 && (j + 1) % w == 0) {
                    matrix[i][j] = -(h * w - 1) * 1000000000L - 1;
                } else {
                    matrix[i][j] = 1000000000L;
                }
            }
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < W; j++) {
                System.out.print(matrix[i][j] + (j == W - 1 ? "" : " "));
            }
            System.out.println();
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03699_0P.java: 1-38 
import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.Arrays;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] s = new int[N];
        int totalSum = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            s[i] = sc.nextInt();
            totalSum += s[i];
        }

        if (totalSum % 10 != 0) {
            System.out.println(totalSum);
        } else {
            Arrays.sort(s);
            int maxDisplayedScore = 0;
            boolean foundNonMultipleOf10 = false;
            for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
                if (s[i] % 10 != 0) {
                    maxDisplayedScore = totalSum - s[i];
                    foundNonMultipleOf10 = true;
                    break;
                }
            }

            if (foundNonMultipleOf10) {
                System.out.println(maxDisplayedScore);
            } else {
                System.out.println(0);
            }
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class WordChain {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String A = sc.next();
        String B = sc.next();
        String C = sc.next();
        sc.close();

        boolean condition1 = A.charAt(A.length() - 1) == B.charAt(0);

        boolean condition2 = B.charAt(B.length() - 1) == C.charAt(0);

        if (condition1 && condition2) {
            System.out.println("YES");
        } else {
            System.out.println("NO");
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class ShowerDuration {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long T = sc.nextLong();
        long[] t = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            t[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }
        sc.close();

        long totalDuration = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N - 1; i++) {
            totalDuration += Math.min(T, t[i + 1] - t[i]);
        }
        totalDuration += T;

        System.out.println(totalDuration);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int m = sc.nextInt();
        long[] x = new long[n];
        long[] y = new long[m];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            x[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
            y[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }
        sc.close();

        long MOD = 1000000007;

        long sumWidths = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            sumWidths = (sumWidths + (2L * i - (n - 1)) * x[i]) % MOD;
        }

        long sumHeights = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
            sumHeights = (sumHeights + (2L * i - (m - 1)) * y[i]) % MOD;
        }

        long totalArea = (sumWidths * sumHeights) % MOD;
        if (totalArea < 0) {
            totalArea += MOD;
        }

        System.out.println(totalArea);
    }
}

import java.util.Arrays;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long C = sc.nextLong();
        long K = sc.nextLong();
        long[] T = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            T[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }
        sc.close();

        Arrays.sort(T);

        int buses = 0;
        int i = 0;
        while (i < N) {
            buses++;
            long currentBusDepartureLimit = T[i] + K;
            int passengersOnBus = 0;
            while (i < N && T[i] <= currentBusDepartureLimit && passengersOnBus < C) {
                passengersOnBus++;
                i++;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(buses);
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03814_2P.java: 1-29 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        sc.close();

        int firstA = -1;
        int lastZ = -1;

        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'A') {
                firstA = i;
                break;
            }
        }

        for (int i = s.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'Z') {
                lastZ = i;
                break;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(lastZ - firstA + 1);
    }
}

        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'A') {
                firstA = i;
                break;
            }
        }

        for (int i = s.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'Z') {
                lastZ = i;
                break;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(lastZ - firstA + 1);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long A = sc.nextLong();
        long B = sc.nextLong();

        long[] X = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            X[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long totalFatigue = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < N - 1; i++) {
            long distance = X[i + 1] - X[i];
            long walkCost = distance * A;
            totalFatigue += Math.min(walkCost, B);
        }

        System.out.println(totalFatigue);

        sc.close();
    }
}

        int S = sc.nextInt();
        sc.close();

                    count++;

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long x = sc.nextLong();
        long[] a = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long operations = 0;

        if (a[0] + a[1] > x) {
            long diff = (a[0] + a[1]) - x;
            operations += diff;
            a[1] = Math.max(0, a[1] - diff);
        }

        for (int i = 1; i < N - 1; i++) {
            if (a[i] + a[i + 1] > x) {
                long diff = (a[i] + a[i + 1]) - x;
                operations += diff;
                a[i + 1] = Math.max(0, a[i + 1] - diff);
            }
        }

        System.out.println(operations);
        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long T = sc.nextLong();
        long[] A = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            A[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        long maxProfit = 0;
        long minPrice = A[0];
        for (int i = 1; i < N; i++) {
            maxProfit = Math.max(maxProfit, A[i] - minPrice);
            minPrice = Math.min(minPrice, A[i]);
        }

        long count = 0;
        minPrice = A[0];
        for (int i = 1; i < N; i++) {
            if (A[i] - minPrice == maxProfit) {
                count++;
            }
            minPrice = Math.min(minPrice, A[i]);
        }

        System.out.println(count);
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p03972_1P.java: 1-56 
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int H = sc.nextInt();

        List<Edge> edges = new ArrayList<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < W; i++) {
            long p = sc.nextLong();
            edges.add(new Edge(p, 0));
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            long q = sc.nextLong();
            edges.add(new Edge(q, 1));
        }

        Collections.sort(edges);

        long totalCost = 0;
        long pavedHorizontalRoads = 0;
        long pavedVerticalRoads = 0;

        for (Edge edge : edges) {
            if (edge.type == 0) {
                totalCost += edge.cost * (H + 1 - pavedVerticalRoads);
                pavedHorizontalRoads++;
            } else {
                totalCost += edge.cost * (W + 1 - pavedHorizontalRoads);
                pavedVerticalRoads++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(totalCost);
        sc.close();
    }

    static class Edge implements Comparable<Edge> {
        long cost;
        int type;

        public Edge(long cost, int type) {
            this.cost = cost;
            this.type = type;
        }

        @Override
        public int compareTo(Edge other) {
            return Long.compare(this.cost, other.cost);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int W = sc.nextInt();
        int H = sc.nextInt();

        List<Edge> edges = new ArrayList<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < W; i++) {
            long p = sc.nextLong();
            edges.add(new Edge(p, 0));
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < H; i++) {
            long q = sc.nextLong();
            edges.add(new Edge(q, 1));
        }

        Collections.sort(edges);

        long minCost = 0;
        long horizontalPavedCount = 0;
        long verticalPavedCount = 0;

        for (Edge edge : edges) {
            if (edge.type == 0) {
                minCost += edge.cost * (H + 1 - verticalPavedCount);
                horizontalPavedCount++;
            } else {
                minCost += edge.cost * (W + 1 - horizontalPavedCount);
                verticalPavedCount++;
            }
        }

        System.out.println(minCost);
        sc.close();
    }

    static class Edge implements Comparable<Edge> {
        long cost;
        int type;

        public Edge(long cost, int type) {
            this.cost = cost;
            this.type = type;
        }

        @Override
        public int compareTo(Edge other) {
            return Long.compare(this.cost, other.cost);
        }
    }
}

import java.util.HashMap;
import java.util.Map;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();

        Map<Character, Integer> firstLetterCounts = new HashMap<>();

        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            String P_i = sc.next();
            char firstChar = P_i.charAt(0);
            firstLetterCounts.put(firstChar, firstLetterCounts.getOrDefault(firstChar, 0) + 1);
        }

        long totalKUPCs = 0;
        for (int count : firstLetterCounts.values()) {
            totalKUPCs += count / K;
        }

        System.out.println(totalKUPCs);

        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p04001_3P.java: 1-28 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        long totalSum = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < (1 << (s.length() - 1)); i++) {
            long currentSum = 0;
            long currentNumber = 0;

            for (int j = 0; j < s.length(); j++) {
                currentNumber = currentNumber * 10 + (s.charAt(j) - '0');

                if (j < s.length() - 1 && ((i >> j) & 1) == 1) {
                    currentSum += currentNumber;
                    currentNumber = 0;
                }
            }
            currentSum += currentNumber;
            totalSum += currentSum;
        }
        System.out.println(totalSum);
        sc.close();
    }
}
test/1/gemini_p03999_4P.java: 1-30 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        long totalSum = 0;

        for (int i = 0; i < (1 << (s.length() - 1)); i++) {
            long currentFormulaSum = 0;
            long currentNumber = 0;

            for (int j = 0; j < s.length(); j++) {
                currentNumber = currentNumber * 10 + (s.charAt(j) - '0');

                if (j < s.length() - 1 && ((i >> j) & 1) == 1) {
                    currentFormulaSum += currentNumber;
                    currentNumber = 0;
                }
            }
            currentFormulaSum += currentNumber;
            totalSum += currentFormulaSum;
        }

        System.out.println(totalSum);
        sc.close();
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.next();
        sc.close();

        boolean hasN = false;
        boolean hasS = false;
        boolean hasE = false;
        boolean hasW = false;

        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            if (c == 'N') {
                hasN = true;
            } else if (c == 'S') {
                hasS = true;
            } else if (c == 'E') {
                hasE = true;
            } else if (c == 'W') {
                hasW = true;
            }
        }

        if ((hasN == hasS) && (hasE == hasW)) {
            System.out.println("Yes");
        } else {
            System.out.println("No");
        }
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int[] a = new int[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextInt();
        }
        sc.close();

        long minCost = Long.MAX_VALUE;

        for (int y = -101; y <= 101; y++) {
            long currentCost = 0;
            for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
                currentCost += (long) Math.pow(a[i] - y, 2);
            }
            minCost = Math.min(minCost, currentCost);
        }

        System.out.println(minCost);
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p04035_0P.java: 1-42 
import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.List;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        long L = sc.nextLong();
        long[] a = new long[N];
        for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
            a[i] = sc.nextLong();
        }

        int targetKnot = -1;
        for (int i = 0; i < N - 1; i++) {
            if (a[i] + a[i + 1] >= L) {
                targetKnot = i;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (targetKnot == -1) {
            System.out.println("Impossible");
        } else {
            System.out.println("Possible");
            List<Integer> result = new ArrayList<>();
            for (int i = 0; i < targetKnot; i++) {
                result.add(i + 1);
            }
            for (int i = N - 2; i >= targetKnot; i--) {
                result.add(i + 1);
            }

            for (int knot : result) {
                System.out.println(knot);
            }
        }
        sc.close();
    }
}

train/1/gemini_p04039_3P.java: 1-42 
import java.util.HashSet;
import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.Set;

public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        Set<Integer> dislikedDigits = new HashSet<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < K; i++) {
            dislikedDigits.add(sc.nextInt());
        }

        int amount = N;
        while (true) {
            if (isValid(amount, dislikedDigits)) {
                System.out.println(amount);
                break;
            }
            amount++;
        }
        sc.close();
    }

    private static boolean isValid(int num, Set<Integer> dislikedDigits) {
        if (num == 0) {
            return !dislikedDigits.contains(0);
        }
        int temp = num;
        while (temp > 0) {
            int digit = temp % 10;
            if (dislikedDigits.contains(digit)) {
                return false;
            }
            temp /= 10;
        }
        return true;
    }
}
test/1/gemini_p04039_2P.java: 1-43 
import java.util.Scanner;
import java.util.Set;
import java.util.HashSet;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int N = sc.nextInt();
        int K = sc.nextInt();
        Set<Integer> dislikedDigits = new HashSet<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < K; i++) {
            dislikedDigits.add(sc.nextInt());
        }

        int amount = N;
        while (true) {
            if (isValid(amount, dislikedDigits)) {
                System.out.println(amount);
                break;
            }
            amount++;
        }

        sc.close();
    }

    private static boolean isValid(int num, Set<Integer> dislikedDigits) {
        if (num == 0) {
            return !dislikedDigits.contains(0);
        }

        int temp = num;
        while (temp > 0) {
            int digit = temp % 10;
            if (dislikedDigits.contains(digit)) {
                return false;
            }
            temp /= 10;
        }
        return true;
    }
}

train/1/claude_p00444_4P.java: 1-26 
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int[] coins = {500, 100, 50, 10, 5, 1};

        while (true) {
            int amount = sc.nextInt();
            if (amount == 0) break;

            int change = 1000 - amount;
            int totalCoins = 0;

            for (int coin : coins) {
                totalCoins += change / coin;
                change %= coin;
            }

            System.out.println(totalCoins);
        }

        sc.close();
    }
}
